source.expression: let    Source = UsageMetricsDataConnector.GetMetricsData(BaseUrl & '/metadata/v201906/metrics/workspace/' & WorkspaceId & '/reportviews'),    metricsTable = Table.FromRecords(Source),    checkForEmptyTable = if Table.IsEmpty(metricsTable) then                        Table.FromRows                        (                            {                            },                            {                                'ReportId', 'ReportType', 'ReportName', 'AppName', 'UserKey', 'UserId', 'UserAgent', 'DatasetName', 'DistributionMethod', 'CapacityId', 'CapacityName', 'CreationTime', 'ConsumptionMethod'                            }                        )                        else                        metricsTable,    finalTable = Table.TransformColumnTypes(checkForEmptyTable, {{'CreationTime', type datetime}}),    #'Renamed Columns' = Table.RenameColumns(finalTable,{{'ConsumptionMethod', 'OriginalConsumptionMethod'}}),    #'Replaced Value' = Table.ReplaceValue(#'Renamed Columns','Apps','App',Replacer.ReplaceText,{'DistributionMethod'})in    #'Replaced Value'

measures.name: Report views
measures.expression: COUNTROWS('Report views') + 0

measures.name: Report viewers
measures.expression: DISTINCTCOUNT('Report views'[UserKey]) + 0

measures.name: Page view share
measures.expression: DIVIDE(COUNTROWS('Report page views'), CALCULATE(COUNTROWS('Report page views'), ALL('Report pages'[SectionName])), 0)

measures.name: View trend
measures.expression: var numberOfDays = DATEDIFF(MIN('Report views'[Date]), MAX('Report views'[Date]),DAY) + 1var periodLength = INT(numberOfDays/2) - 1var firstPeriod = CALCULATE([Report views], DATESBETWEEN('Report views'[Date], MIN('Report views'[Date]), MIN('Report views'[Date]) + periodLength))var secondPeriod = CALCULATE([Report views], DATESBETWEEN('Report views'[Date], MAX('Report views'[Date]) - periodLength, MAX('Report views'[Date])))return DIVIDE(secondPeriod - firstPeriod, firstPeriod)  + 0

measures.name: P-50
measures.expression: PERCENTILE.INC('Report load times'[loadTime], 0.5) + 0

measures.name: P-50 7d
measures.expression: CALCULATE([P-50], ALL(Dates), DATESINPERIOD('Report load times'[Date], max('Report load times'[Date]), -7, DAY)) + 0

measures.name: P-25
measures.expression: PERCENTILE.INC('Report load times'[loadTime], 0.25) + 0

measures.name: P-10
measures.expression: PERCENTILE.INC('Report load times'[loadTime], 0.1) + 0

measures.name: P-90 7d
measures.expression: CALCULATE([P-90], ALL(Dates), DATESINPERIOD('Report load times'[Date], max('Report load times'[Date]), -7, DAY)) + 0

measures.name: P-10 7d
measures.expression: CALCULATE([P-10], DATESINPERIOD('Report load times'[Date], max('Report load times'[Date]), -7, DAY)) + 0

measures.name: Typical report opening interval
measures.expression: IF(ISBLANK(MAX('Report load times'[loadTime]) ),     'This report has no performance measurements.',    IF(HASONEVALUE('Report load times'[loadTime]),         'This report only has a single performance measurement. The load time was ' & MAX('Report load times'[loadTime]) & ' seconds.',         IF([P-10] = [P-50] = [P-25],             'Across all measurements, this report loaded in  ' & MAX('Report load times'[loadTime]) & ' seconds.',             'For most of the users your report opens within ' & INT([P-10 7d]) & ' and ' & INT([P-90 7d]) & ' seconds.' )))

measures.name: Rank string
measures.expression: IF(HASONEVALUE(Reports[ReportGuid]), IF(ISBLANK(MAX('Report rank'[ReportRank])), '', 'Rank ' & MAX('Report rank'[ReportRank]) & ' across '& [Total Org Report Count] & ' reports in the organization'), '')

measures.name: Performance trend
measures.expression: var numberOfDays = DATEDIFF(MIN('Report views'[Date]), MAX('Report views'[Date]),DAY) + 1var periodLength = INT(numberOfDays/2) - 1var firstPeriod = CALCULATE([P-50], DATESBETWEEN('Report load times'[Date], MIN('Report load times'[Date]), MIN('Report load times'[Date]) + periodLength))var secondPeriod = CALCULATE([P-50], DATESBETWEEN('Report load times'[Date], MAX('Report load times'[Date]) - periodLength, MAX('Report load times'[Date])))return DIVIDE(secondPeriod - firstPeriod, firstPeriod) + 0 * -1

measures.name: Workspace report viewers
measures.expression: DISTINCTCOUNT('Workspace views'[UserKey]) + 0
measures.description: Total number of unique viewers of all reports in the workspace

measures.name: Workspace inactive reports
measures.expression: CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('Workspace reports'[ReportGuid]), 'Workspace reports'[Days with usage] = 0) + 0

measures.name: Workspace views

measures.name: Workspace active days per report

measures.name: Workspace reports

measures.name: Workspace active reports

measures.description: Number of reports with views in the last 30 days

measures.name: Workspace report view %

measures.name: Covered time display string
measures.expression: IF(ISBLANK(MAX('Report views'[CreationTime])), 'No usage data', 'Report usage based on data from ' & DATE(  YEAR(MIN('Report views'[CreationTime])),  MONTH(MIN('Report views'[CreationTime])),  DAY(MIN('Report views'[CreationTime]))) & ' to ' & DATE(  YEAR(MAX('Report views'[CreationTime])),  MONTH(MAX('Report views'[CreationTime])),  DAY(MAX('Report views'[CreationTime]))))

measures.name: Embedding for your organziation
measures.expression: CALCULATE([Report views], 'Report views'[OriginalConsumptionMethod] = 'Embedding for your organization')

measures.name: Embedding for your customers
measures.expression: CALCULATE([Report views], 'Report views'[OriginalConsumptionMethod] = 'Embedding for your customers')

measures.name: Simplified embedding
measures.expression: CALCULATE([Report views], 'Report views'[OriginalConsumptionMethod] = 'Simplified embedding')

measures.name: Workspace view trend
measures.expression: var startDate = CALCULATE(MIN('Dates'[Date]), ALL('Dates'))var endDate = CALCULATE(MAX('Dates'[Date]), ALL('Dates'))var numberOfDays = DATEDIFF(startDate, endDate, DAY) + 1var periodLength = INT(numberOfDays/2) - 1var middleDate1 =  CALCULATE(LASTDATE(DATESBETWEEN('Dates'[Date], startDate, startDate + periodLength)) , ALL('Dates'))var middleDate2 =  CALCULATE(FIRSTDATE(DATESBETWEEN('Report views'[Date], endDate - periodLength, endDate)), ALL('Dates'))var firstPeriod = CALCULATE([Report views], ALL('Dates'), DATESBETWEEN('Report views'[Date], startDate, middleDate1))var secondPeriod = CALCULATE([Report views], ALL('Dates'), DATESBETWEEN('Report views'[Date], middleDate2, endDate))//return startDate & '  ' & middleDate1 & ' ' & middleDate2 & '  ' & numberOfDays & ', ' & periodLength & ': ' & firstPeriod & '  ' & secondPeriodreturn DIVIDE(secondPeriod - firstPeriod, firstPeriod, 0)

measures.name: Last refresh time display string
measures.expression: IF(ISBLANK(MAX('Refresh Stats'[Last Refresh])), \t'Usage data has not been imported yet. Check the refresh history and data source credentials in the Usage Metrics Report dataset settings.', \tIF(DATEVALUE(MAX('Refresh Stats'[Last Refresh])) < DATE(2019,11,20),\t'Usage data has not been imported yet. Check the refresh history and data source credentials in the Usage Metrics Report dataset settings.', \tIF(DATEDIFF(MAX('Refresh Stats'[Last Refresh]), TODAY(), day ) > 4, \t\t'The usage data is outdated. Check the refresh history and data source credentials in the Usage Metrics Report dataset settings.', \t\t'Dataset last refreshed: ' & MAX('Refresh Stats'[Last Refresh]) & ' (UTC)')))

tables.name: FP Capacity
tables.description: This is the weekly headcount of FPs.

measures.name: Curr Cap
measures.expression: VAR current_year = MAX('FP Capacity'[Year])RETURNCALCULATE(SUM('FP Capacity'[FP Capacity]),FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk','RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Week]='RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Current Wk]),FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk','RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Year]=current_year))

measures.name: PYTD Cap
measures.expression: VAR previous_year = MAX('FP Capacity'[Year])-1RETURNCALCULATE(SUM('FP Capacity'[FP Capacity]),    FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk','RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Week]='RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Current Wk]),    FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk',VALUE('RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Year])=previous_year))

measures.name: PYE Cap
measures.expression: VAR previous_year = MAX('CP+'[Year])-1RETURNCALCULATE(SUM('FP Capacity'[FP Capacity]),    FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk','RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Week]=52),    FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk',VALUE('RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Year])=previous_year))

measures.name: PYTD Var
measures.expression: CALCULATE(('FP Capacity'[Curr Cap]-'FP Capacity'[PYTD Cap])/'FP Capacity'[PYTD Cap])

measures.name: PYE Var

measures.name: PYTD NFR Cap

tables.name: FP Contracts
tables.description: This a weekly, cumulative count of new FP contracts each year.

measures.name: YTD FA Contracts
measures.expression: VAR current_year = MAX('FP Contracts'[Year])RETURNCALCULATE(SUM('FP Contracts'[FP Contracts]),    FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk','RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Week]='RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Current Wk]),    FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk','RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Year]=current_year))

measures.name: PYTD FA Contracts
measures.expression: VAR previous_year = MAX('FP Contracts'[Year])-1RETURNCALCULATE(SUM('FP Contracts'[FP Contracts]),    FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk','RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Week]='RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Current Wk]),    FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk',VALUE('RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Year])=previous_year))

columns.name: Type
columns.expression: SWITCH(WMFC_CD[Category],'FR', 'FAs and Associate Reps','FR-WA', 'FAs and Associate Reps','FR-FC', 'FAs and Associate Reps', 'Associate Representative', 'FAs and Associate Reps','Associate-Regular', 'Associates','Associate-Insurance', 'Associates','Associate-Securities', 'Associates', 'Support Associate', 'Associates', 'Other Associates', 'Associates','Insurance Producer', 'Insurance Prod.','OP-Licensed', 'Office Professionals','OP-Unlicensed', 'Office Professionals','Field Leader', 'Field Leaders', 'TFGT-Licensed', 'Virtual Advice', 'TFGT-Unlicensed', 'Virtual Advice')

columns.name: Category Desc
columns.expression: SWITCH(WMFC_CD[Category],'FR', 'FA','FR-WA', 'FA-WA','FR-FC', 'FA-FC', 'Associate Representative', 'Associate Representative','Associate-Regular', 'Associate-Regular','Associate-Insurance', 'Associate-Insurance','Associate-Securities', 'Associate-Securities', 'Support Associate', 'Support Associate', 'Other Associates', 'Other Associates','Insurance Producer', 'Insurance Producer','OP-Licensed', 'OP-Licensed','OP-Unlicensed', 'OP-Unlicensed','Field Leader', 'Field Leader', 'TFGT-Licensed', 'VA-Licensed', 'TFGT-Unlicensed', 'VA-Unlicensed')

measures.name: PY2E
measures.expression: VAR previous_year2 = MAX('RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Year])-2RETURNCALCULATE(SUM(WMFC_CD[WMFC]),    FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk','RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Week]=52),    FILTER('RFO-Mkt-Wk',VALUE('RFO-Mkt-Wk'[Year])=previous_year2))

measures.name: Curr

columns.name: FP Tenure - NFP, Vet
columns.expression: if(not('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000', '002010', '002022', '002024', '002025', '002026', '002027', '003100', '003500'}), 'Other',if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] = '002010', 'Associate Rep',if((('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date]) / 365.25) < 4, 'NFA', 'VET')))

columns.name: FP Tenure - NFP 4 Mo

columns.name: Leader Role
columns.expression: if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] = '001004', 'RD',if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] = '001005', 'RDL', if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] = '001007', 'RDD')))

columns.name: FP Tenure - NFP 6 Mo

columns.name: FA Tenure

columns.name: Cal_YTD_Flag
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Sunday], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'CURRENT'), True, False)

columns.name: Cal_PYTD_Flag
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[PYTD DATE], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'PREVIOUS'), True, False)

columns.name: PYTD Flag two Sundays
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[PYTD DATE two Sundays], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_NBR] = DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Year]), True, False)

columns.name: YTD Flag two Sundays
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[Two Sundays Ago], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_NBR] = DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year]), True, False)

measures.name: Current Date
measures.expression: today()

measures.name: Current Year
measures.expression: LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT],'CURRENT')

measures.name: Prior YEar
measures.expression: DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year] - 1

measures.name: PYTD DATE
measures.expression: (LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_END_DT], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today() - 5)) - 364

measures.name: Prior Year 2
measures.expression: DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year] - 2

measures.name: PYTD DATE two Sundays
measures.expression: (LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_END_DT], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today() - 379))

measures.name: Days into Year
measures.expression: CALCULATE(COUNT(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[YTD Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: Days in Year
measures.expression: CALCULATE(COUNT(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.expression: calculate(52-MAX(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[YTD Flag two Sundays] in {TRUE})

measures.name: Current Week Number
measures.expression: LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Week Flag],'TRUE')

measures.name: YTD WID
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'WID',     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: CY ANBP
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),        DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE},        ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'ANBP')

measures.name: CY OtherRev
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),    DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE},     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'OtherRev')

measures.name: PY ANBP
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_Flag] in {TRUE},    ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'ANBP')

measures.name: PY WID
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_Flag] in {TRUE},     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'WID')

measures.name: PY2 ANBP
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_2_Flag] in {TRUE},     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'ANBP')

measures.name: PY2 WID
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_2_Flag] in {TRUE},     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'WID')

measures.name: PYTD ANBP
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'ANBP',     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_PYTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: PYTD WID
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'WID',     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_PYTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: ANBP YOY Change
measures.expression: DIVIDE(([CY ANBP] - ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD ANBP]),ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD ANBP])

measures.name: WID YOY Change
measures.expression: DIVIDE((ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD WID] - ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD WID]),ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD WID])

measures.name: YTD OtherRev running total in CalWk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(\t[YTD WID], \tFILTER(\t\tALLSELECTED('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]),\t\tISONORAFTER('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk], MAX('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]), DESC)\t))

measures.name: PYTD OtherRev running total in CalWk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(\t[PYTD WID],\tFILTER(\t\tALLSELECTED('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]),\t\tISONORAFTER('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk], MAX('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]), DESC)\t))

measures.name: PY2 OtherRev running total in CalWk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(\t[PY2 WID],\tFILTER(\t\tALLSELECTED('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]),\t\tISONORAFTER('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk], MAX('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]), DESC)\t))

measures.name: PY OtherRev running total in CalWk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(\t[PY WID],\tFILTER(\t\tALLSELECTED('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]),\t\tISONORAFTER('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk], MAX('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]), DESC)\t))

measures.name: YTD_OtherRev_Cummulative
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD OtherRev running total in CalWk],    DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: ANBP/Appt
measures.expression: divide([CY ANBP],'Appointments/PC/JFW'[YTD Appointments])

measures.name: WID 4 Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD WID],4),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Prior 4 Weeks Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: WID Curr Wk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD WID],'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_TXT]='PREVIOUS')

measures.name: OtherREV YTD Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD WID],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_NBR])),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: ANBP 4 Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[CY ANBP],4),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Prior 4 Weeks Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: ANBP Curr Wk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[CY ANBP],'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_TXT] = 'PREVIOUS')

measures.name: ANBP YTD Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[CY ANBP],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_NBR])),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: 4wk ANBP Gap
measures.expression: YTD_GOALS_DD[Weekly Need ANBP]-ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP 4 Wk Average]

measures.name: 4wk Other Rev Gap
measures.expression: YTD_GOALS_DD[Weekly Need WID]-ANBP_OtherRev_DD[WID 4 Wk Average]

measures.name: 4wk ANBP (LH) Gap
measures.expression: YTD_GOALS_DD[Weekly Need ANBP (LH)]-ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP 4 Wk Average]

measures.name: YTD Total Sales
measures.expression: ANBP_OtherRev_DD[CY ANBP]+ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD WID]

measures.name: Total Sales YOY Change
measures.expression: DIVIDE((ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD Total Sales] - ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD Total Sales]),ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD Total Sales])

measures.name: PYTD Total Sales
measures.expression: ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD ANBP]+ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD WID]

measures.name: PY Total Sales
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: PY2 Total Sales
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_2_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: YTD NFP Capacity
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    SUM(Capacity[Capacity]),    'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[YTD Flag] in {True},    'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Current',    'Capacity'[Type] in {'NFR','Red Role'},    'Capacity'[RFO_ID]<>'0716')

measures.name: YTD Vet Capacity
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    SUM(Capacity[Capacity]),    'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[YTD Flag] in {True},    'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Current',    'Capacity'[Type] in {'Vet'},    'Capacity'[RFO_ID]<>'0716')

measures.name: YTD Total NFP+Vet Capacity

measures.name: YTD Capacity TOTAL

columns.name: Contract Min Week any year
columns.expression: VAR ContractMinWeek = CALCULATE(        MIN(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),        ALLEXCEPT(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[BenefitContractNumber])    )   RETURNIF((RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]=ContractMinWeek),'Contract MinWeek','Not Contract MinWeek')

measures.name: Received CW
measures.expression: //VAR MaxWeek = WEEKNUM(CALCULATE(//            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))//VAR MaxYear = YEAR(CALCULATE(//            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))//RETURN//    CALCULATE(//        SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),//            FILTER(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,WEEKNUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])=MaxWeek && YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])=MaxYear))+0Var max_week = CALCULATE(    MAX(DTRB_PERF_DATES[WeekIndex]),    FILTER(DTRB_PERF_DATES, DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]=(TODAY())))-1Var MaxDay= CALCULATE(MAX(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]),FILTER(DTRB_PERF_DATES,DTRB_PERF_DATES[WeekIndex]=max_week))VAR start_week = max_week VAR StartDay=CALCULATE(MIN(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]),FILTER(DTRB_PERF_DATES,DTRB_PERF_DATES[WeekIndex]=start_week))returnCALCULATE(SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),  RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[TransReceiveDt]<= MaxDay,RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[TransReceiveDt]>=StartDay)

measures.name: Received YTD
measures.expression: //VAR MaxYear = YEAR(CALCULATE(//            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))//RETURN//CALCULATE(//   SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),//    FILTER((RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE),//        YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])=MaxYear))+0CALCULATE(   SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),   DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_YTD_Flag]={TRUE()},RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Contract Min Week any year]='Contract MinWeek')

measures.name: Received PYTD
measures.expression: //var py = YEAR(CALCULATE(            //MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))-1//var cw = WEEKNUM(CALCULATE(            //MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))//RETURN//CALCULATE(//SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),//FILTER(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,//YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])=py//&& WEEKNUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])<=cw//)//)+0CALCULATE(SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_PYTD_Flag] in {TRUE},RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Contract Min Week any year]='Contract MinWeek')

measures.name: Estimated Sales Credit CW
measures.expression: VAR MaxWeek = CALCULATE(MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE))RETURNCALCULATE(SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Est Sales Credits]),FILTER(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]=MaxWeek&& RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Pending]=1))+0

measures.name: Pending Count CW
measures.expression: VAR MaxWeek = CALCULATE(            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE))RETURN    CALCULATE(        SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Pending]),            FILTER((RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE),RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]=MaxWeek))+0

measures.name: Estimated Sales Credit by Week
measures.expression: CALCULATE(SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Est Sales Credits]),FILTER(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]=MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])&& RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Pending]=1))

measures.name: Received 4 Wk Total Week_Index DistDt
measures.expression: Var max_week = CALCULATE(    MAX(DTRB_PERF_DATES[WeekIndex]),    FILTER(DTRB_PERF_DATES, DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]=(TODAY())))-1Var MaxDay= CALCULATE(MAX(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]),FILTER(DTRB_PERF_DATES,DTRB_PERF_DATES[WeekIndex]=max_week))VAR start_week = max_week -3VAR StartDay=CALCULATE(MIN(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]),FILTER(DTRB_PERF_DATES,DTRB_PERF_DATES[WeekIndex]=start_week))RETURNCALCULATE(              SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),              RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[TransReceiveDt]>=StartDay && RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[TransReceiveDt]<=MaxDay )

measures.name: Received 4 Week Avg
measures.expression: DIVIDE([Received 4 Wk Total Week_Index DistDt],4)

measures.name: Received YoY
measures.expression: divide([Received YTD]-[Received PYTD],[Received PYTD])

measures.name: Pending CY
measures.expression: var MaxPendYear = CALCULATE(    YEAR(MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE))RETURNCALCULATE(    SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Pending]),    FILTER(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])=MaxPendYear))

measures.name: Pending PY
measures.expression: var MaxPendYear = CALCULATE(    YEAR(MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE))RETURNCALCULATE(    SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Pending]),    FILTER(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])=MaxPendYear-1))

measures.name: Pending PY2
measures.expression: var MaxPendYear = CALCULATE(    YEAR(MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE))RETURNCALCULATE(    SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Pending]),    FILTER(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])=MaxPendYear-2))

measures.name: Received CY
measures.expression: CALCULATE(   SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),   DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_YTD_Flag]={TRUE()},RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Contract Min Week any year]='Contract MinWeek')

measures.name: Received PY

measures.name: Prior Year NC
measures.expression: CALCULATE( sum('New Clients'[FIN_CUST_PNT_VLU]), DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Year Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: Prior Year 2 NC
measures.expression: CALCULATE( sum('New Clients'[FIN_CUST_PNT_VLU]), DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Year 2 Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: PYTD NC
measures.expression: var prev2weeknum = LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Two Sundays Ago]))ReturnCALCULATE(sum('New Clients'[FIN_CUST_PNT_VLU]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Year Flag] in {TRUE},DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR]<=prev2weeknum)

measures.name: YTD_NC
measures.expression: calculate( sum('New Clients'[FIN_CUST_PNT_VLU]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[YTD Flag two Sundays] in {TRUE})

measures.name: YOY Change NC
measures.expression: (([YTD_NC] - [PYTD NC])/([PYTD NC]))

measures.name: New Client 4 Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide('New Clients'[YTD_NC],4),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Prior 4 Weeks Flag NC] in {TRUE},DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: 4 Wk Gap New Clients
measures.expression: [Weekly Need New Clients]-'New Clients'[New Client 4 Wk Average]

columns.name: Current Week
columns.expression: if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] = today(), 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Calendar Year Week Number])

columns.name: Current Week Flag
columns.expression: if(lookupvalue('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Calendar Year Week Number], 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date], today()) = 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Calendar Year Week Number], True, FALSE)

columns.name: Division
columns.expression: if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical RFO] IN {'0283', '0365', '0435', '0496', '0810'}, 'Central', if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical RFO] IN {'0115', '0165', '0190', '0240', '0361', '0384'}, 'East', if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical RFO] IN {'0291', '0410', '0475', '0525', '0529'}, 'West', 'Other')))

columns.name: Region
columns.expression: IF('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical RFO] IN {'0361', '0365', '0435', '0496'}, 'Established', IF('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical RFO] IN {'0165', '0240', '0283', '0291', '0410', '0525'}, 'Growth', IF('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical RFO] IN {'0115', '0190', '0384', '0475', '0529'}, 'Invest', IF('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical RFO] = '0716', 'TAN',IF('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical RFO] = '0810', 'Colorado Springs', '')))))

columns.name: Current Year Flag
columns.expression: if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Calendar Year Name] = 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Current Year], True, False)

columns.name: Prior Year Flag
columns.expression: if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Calendar Year Name] = 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Prior Year], True, False)

columns.name: Prior Year 2 Flag
columns.expression: if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Calendar Year Name] = 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Prior Year 2], True, False)

columns.name: Prior Week Flag
columns.expression: if(LOOKUPVALUE('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Calendar Year Week Number], 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date], today() - 7) = 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Calendar Year Week Number], 'True')

columns.name: FP Tenure - NFP1-4, Vet, Other
columns.expression: if(not('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000', '002010', '002020', '002021', '002022', '002024', '002025', '002026', '002027', '003100', '003500'}), 'Other',    if(('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 1, 'NFP1',     if(('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 2, 'NFP2',     if(('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 3, 'NFP3',     if(('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 4, 'NFP4',     'Vet')))))

columns.name: Appointment Type Code (groups)
columns.expression: SWITCH(  TRUE,  ISBLANK('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Type Code]),  '(Blank)',  'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Type Code] IN {'Connect'},  'Connect',  'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Type Code] IN {'Gather Data'},  'Gather Data',  'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Type Code] IN {'Business Planning/QBR',    'Call Clinic',    'Career Overview',    'Case Development',    'COI',    'Final Interview',    'First Interview',    'Lunch and Learn',    'Networking',    'One-on-One',    'Other',    'Out of Office',    'Personal',    'Recruiting',    'Second Interview',    'Third Interview',    'Training',    'UNK',    'Workshop/Client Appreciation'},  'Other',  'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Type Code] IN {'Review'},  'Review',  'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Type Code] IN {'Service'},  'Service',  'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Type Code] IN {'Strategy Call/Meeting'},  'Strategy Call/Meeting',  'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Type Code] IN {'Take Action'},  'Take Action',  'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Type Code])

columns.name: TOP 10 - FP Tenure - NFP1-4, Vet, Other
columns.expression: if(not('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000', '002016', '002022', '002024', '002025', '002026', '002027', '003100', '003500'}), 'Other',    if((DTRB_PERF_DATES[Previous Sunday Date2] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 1, 'NFP1',     if((DTRB_PERF_DATES[Previous Sunday Date2] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 2, 'NFP2',     if((DTRB_PERF_DATES[Previous Sunday Date2] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 3, 'NFP3',     if((DTRB_PERF_DATES[Previous Sunday Date2] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 4, 'NFP4',     'Vet')))))

columns.name: FP Tenure - NFP, Vet, Other
columns.expression: if(not('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000', '002010', '002020', '002021', '002022', '002024', '002025', '002026', '002027', '003100', '003500'}), 'Other',    if(('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 4, 'NFP',     'Vet'))

columns.name: FP Tenure - NFP 6 Mo
columns.expression: if(not('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000', '002010', '002022', '002024', '002025', '002026', '002027', '003100', '003500'}), 'Vet', if((('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date]) / 365.25) < 0.5, 'NFP 6 Mo', 'NA'))

columns.name: FA Tenure - NFP, Vet
columns.expression: if(not('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000', '002010', '002022', '002024', '002025', '002026', '002027', '003100', '003500'}), 'Vet',if((('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date]) / 365.25) < 4, 'NFP', 'Vet'))--if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[FP Tenure - NFP1-4, Vet, Other] in {'NFP1', 'NFP2', 'NFP3', 'NFP4'}, 'NFA', 'Vet')

columns.name: FA Tenure - NFA1-4, Associate Rep, Vet, Other NEWEST
columns.expression: if(not('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000', '002010', '002020', '002021', '002022', '002024', '002025', '002026', '002027', '003100', '003500'}), 'Other',    if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] = '002010', 'Associate Rep',    if(('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 1, 'NFA1',     if(('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 2, 'NFA2',     if(('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 3, 'NFA3',     if(('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date])/ 365.25 < 4, 'NFA4',     'Vet'))))))

columns.name: FA Tenure - Assoc Rep, NFA, Vet, Other
columns.expression: if(not('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000', '002010', '002022', '002024', '002025', '002026', '002027', '003100', '003500'}), 'Other',if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] = '002010', 'Associate Rep',if((('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Date] - 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Adjusted Service Date]) / 365.25) < 4, 'NFA', 'VET')))

columns.name: FA Tenure - Associate Rep, NFA, Vet slicer
columns.expression: if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[FA Tenure - Assoc Rep, NFA, Vet, Other] = 'Associate Rep', 'Associate Rep', if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[FA Tenure - Assoc Rep, NFA, Vet, Other] = 'NFA', 'NFA',if('Appointments/PC/JFW'[FA Tenure - Assoc Rep, NFA, Vet, Other] = 'Vet', 'Vet')))

measures.name: Current Week #
measures.expression: FIRSTNONBLANK('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Current Week], 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Current Week])

measures.name: Current Date
measures.expression: today()

measures.name: Current Year
measures.expression: year(today())

measures.name: Prior Year
measures.expression: [DTRB Current Year] - 1--'Appointments & PCs'[Current Year] - 1

measures.name: PYTD Date DELETE
measures.expression: 'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Current Date] - 365

measures.name: PY Appointments
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    DISTINCTCOUNT('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key]),    DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'PREVIOUS')

measures.name: Prior Year 2
measures.expression: [DTRB Current Year] - 2

measures.name: PYTD Appointments
measures.expression: var pytd_end_date = date(    year(LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_DAY_TXT],'Previous'))-1,    month(LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_DAY_TXT],'Previous')),    day(LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_DAY_TXT],'Previous')))var pytd_start_date = date(year(pytd_end_date),1,1)returncalculate(    DISTINCTCOUNT('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key]),    'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[CAL_DAY_DT] <= pytd_end_date,    'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[CAL_DAY_DT] >= pytd_start_date)

measures.name: PY2TD Appointments
measures.expression: var py2td_end_date = date(    year(LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_DAY_TXT],'Previous'))-2,    month(LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_DAY_TXT],'Previous')),    day(LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_DAY_TXT],'Previous')))var py2td_start_date = date(year(py2td_end_date),1,1)returncalculate(    DISTINCTCOUNT('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key]),    'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[CAL_DAY_DT] <= py2td_end_date,    'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[CAL_DAY_DT] >= py2td_start_date)--CALCULATE(    --DISTINCTCOUNT('Appointments & PCs'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key]),    --'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[PY2TD Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: CY Current Week Appointments
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    DISTINCTCOUNT('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key]),    DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_TXT] = 'CURRENT',    DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'CURRENT',    'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[YTD Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: CY Prior Week Appointments

columns.name: Contract Version Number
columns.description: A number used to uniquely identify a version of a specific occurrence.

columns.name: Writing Agent Version Number
columns.description: A number used to uniquely identify a version of a specific occurrence of the Workforce Dimension Detail.

columns.name: Financial Customer Point Status Code
columns.description: A Financial Customer Point Status Code is the alphanumeric value assigned to represent the status of the points awarded for a Financial Customer in an abbreviated form. When using Financial Customer data, current and history rows must both be included.

columns.name: Financial Customer Age
columns.description: Age of the Customer at the time of the Financial customer Event occurance.

columns.name: Age Class Code
columns.description: A Age Classification Code is the alphanumeric value assigned torepresent a category of people based on age in an abbreviated form. ADULT are age of 16 or older. JUV is for those with an age of 15 oryounger

columns.name: Age Class Description
columns.description: A Age Classification Description is the word or phrase thatinterprets the Age Classification Code, making it understandable tousers.

columns.name: Financial Customer Point Value
columns.description: A Financial Customer Point Value is a numeric value of the point that is assigned when a customer meets the Financial Customer eligibility rules.

columns.name: Market
columns.description: An Organization Zone Code is the alphanumeric value assigned torepresent a subsection of a Regional Financial Office.

columns.name: Organization Zone Description
columns.description: An Organization Zone Description is the alphanumeric valuerepresenting the name of a specific subsection of a RegionalFinancial Office.

columns.name: RFO
columns.description: A code that uniquely identifies a Thrivent deparment organization unit.

columns.name: Organization Department Description
columns.description: A character field that describes a Thrivent department organizationunit.

columns.name: Organization Division Code
columns.description: A code that identifies a Thrivent division organization unit.

columns.name: Organization Division Description
columns.description: A text field that identifies a Thrivent division organizational unite.

columns.name: Financial Customer Point Reason Code
columns.description: A Financial Customer Point Reason Code is the alphanumeric value assigned to represent the reason a Financial Customer point was given or was removed.

columns.name: Financial Customer Point Reason Description
columns.description: A Financial Customer Point Reason Description is the word or phrase that interprets the Financial Customer Point Reason Code, making it understandable to users.

columns.name: Financial Customer Point Relationship Code
columns.description: The Financial Customer Point Relationship Code is the alphanumeric value assigned to represent the relationship the customer had to the contract at the time the customer is considered to be a Financial Customer or not.

columns.name: Financial Customer Point Relationship Description
columns.description: A Financial Customer Point Relationship Description is the word or phrase that interprets the Financial Customer Point Relationship Code, making it understandable to users.

columns.name: Member Type Code
columns.description: A code indicating the type of membership of a customer or group ofcustomers.

columns.name: Member Type Description
columns.description: The description of the type of membership of a customer or group ofcustomers.

columns.name: Level 5 Product Line Of Business Subgroup Code
Level 5 Product Line Of Business Subgroup Description
Level 4 Product Line Of Business Group Code
Level 4 Product Line Of Business Group Description
Level 3 Product Line Of Business Code
Level 3 Product Line Of Business Description
Assigned FR
columns.description: The full name of an employee (includes title, first name, middle initial, last name and suffix).  This is also called Member Client from iSTP perspective.

columns.name: Employee First Name
columns.description: The first name of an individual.

columns.name: Employee Last Name
columns.description: The last name of an individual.

columns.name: Adjusted Service Date
columns.description: The date used to calculate an individual's years of service.

columns.name: TS ID
columns.description: An primary identifier associated with an employee. This is the 'TS' identifier assigned to an employee by human resources.

columns.name: Employee Status Type Code
columns.description: A code that describes the relationship a person has with Thrivent regarding employment.

columns.name: Employee Status Type Description
columns.description: Employee status type description describes an employee status type code.  The code specifies the type of relationship a person has with Thrivent with regard to employment.

columns.name: Member Age
columns.description: Current Age of the Customer as calculated using CIF date of birth.  Date of Birth is not shared just the numeric value age.

columns.name: Financial Customer Age Group
columns.description: A calculated age group that a new financial customer would fit into based on their birth date.

columns.name: Distribution Performance Reporting Week End Date
Distribution Performance Reporting Year Week Number
Name
columns.expression: 'New Clients'[Employee Last Name]&', '& 'New Clients'[Employee First Name]

columns.name: Region
columns.expression: IF('New Clients'[RFO] IN {'0361', '0365', '0435', '0496'}, 'Established', IF('New Clients'[RFO] IN {'0165', '0240', '0283', '0291', '0410', '0525'}, 'Growth', IF('New Clients'[RFO] IN {'0115', '0190', '0384', '0475', '0529'}, 'Invest', IF('New Clients'[RFO] = '0383', 'TFGT',IF('New Clients'[RFO] = '0716', 'TAN',IF('New Clients'[RFO] = '0810', 'Colorado Springs',IF('New Clients'[RFO] = '0001', 'Home Office')))))))

columns.name: Column - DO NOT DELETE (used in join)
FP Tenure - NFP, Vet
columns.expression: if(not('New Clients'[Job Type Code] in {'002000', '002010', '002022', '002024', '002025', '002026', '002027', '003100', '003500'}), 'Vet', if((('New Clients'[Calendar Date] - 'New Clients'[Adjusted Service Date]) / 365.25) < 4, 'NFP', 'Vet'))

columns.name: Max Cal Date
columns.expression: CALCULATE(MAX('New Clients'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('New Clients','New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),'New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Current')

columns.expression: LOOKUPVALUE('New Clients'[Distribution Performance Reporting Year Week Number], 'New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_TXT], 'PREVIOUS')

columns.name: Prev2 wk newest
columns.expression: LOOKUPVALUE('New Clients'[Distribution Performance Reporting Year Week Number], 'New Clients'[Calendar Date], today())

measures.name: PY2TD New Clients
measures.expression: var cy_start = CALCULATE(MIN('New Clients'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('New Clients','New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),'New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Current')var cy_end = CALCULATE(MAX('New Clients'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('New Clients','New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),'New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Current')var py2_start = date(YEAR(cy_start)-2,MONTH(cy_start),DAY(cy_start))var py2_end = DATE(YEAR(cy_end)-2,MONTH(cy_end),DAY(cy_end))RETURNCALCULATE(SUM('New Clients'[Financial Customer Point Value]), 'New Clients', 'New Clients'[Calendar Date] <= py2_end && 'New Clients'[Calendar Date] >= py2_start)

measures.name: CY PW1 (Full Wk) New Clients
measures.expression: var prev2wknbr = LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today()) - 2returnCALCULATE(    SUM('New Clients'[Financial Customer Point Value]),    DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'Current',    DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR] = prev2wknbr)

measures.name: PY New Clients
measures.expression: var py_start = CALCULATE(MIN('New Clients'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('New Clients','New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),'New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Previous')var py_end = CALCULATE(MAX('New Clients'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('New Clients','New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),'New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Previous')RETURNCALCULATE(SUM('New Clients'[Financial Customer Point Value]), 'New Clients', 'New Clients'[Calendar Date] <= py_end && 'New Clients'[Calendar Date] >= py_start)

measures.name: PY2 New Clients
measures.expression: var py_start = CALCULATE(MIN('New Clients'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('New Clients','New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),'New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Previous')var py_end = CALCULATE(MAX('New Clients'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('New Clients','New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),'New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Previous')var py2_start= date(year(py_start)-1,month(py_start),day(py_start))var py2_end= date(year(py_end)-1,month(py_end),day(py_end))RETURNCALCULATE(SUM('New Clients'[Financial Customer Point Value]), 'New Clients', 'New Clients'[Calendar Date] <= py2_end && 'New Clients'[Calendar Date] >= py2_start)

measures.name: PYTD New Clients
measures.expression: var py_start = CALCULATE(MIN('New Clients'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('New Clients','New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),'New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Previous')var cy_end = CALCULATE(MAX('New Clients'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('New Clients','New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),'New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Current')var py_end = DATE(YEAR(cy_end)-1,MONTH(cy_end),DAY(cy_end))RETURNCALCULATE(SUM('New Clients'[Financial Customer Point Value]), 'New Clients', 'New Clients'[Calendar Date] <= py_end && 'New Clients'[Calendar Date] >= py_start)

measures.name: CY PW2 (Full Wk) New Clients
measures.expression: var prev3wknbr = LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today()) -3var date_3wk_ago = LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_DAY_TXT],'Current') - 21var p3wk_end_date = LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_END_DT],DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],date_3wk_ago)returnCALCULATE(    SUM('New Clients'[Financial Customer Point Value]),    DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'Current',     DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR] = prev3wknbr)        --DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= p3wk_end_date)

measures.name: 4 Wk Total Week Index
measures.expression: Var max_week = CALCULATE(    MAX('New Clients'[WeekIndex]) -1 )VAR start_week = max_week -3RETURNCALCULATE(              SUM('New Clients'[Financial Customer Point Value]),               FILTER('New Clients',               'New Clients'[WeekIndex] >= start_week              && 'New Clients'[WeekIndex] <= max_week))

measures.name: PY PW1 (Full Wk) New Clients
measures.expression: var prev2wknbr = 52--LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today()) - 2--LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],MAX('DTRB_PERF_DATES'[CAL_DAY_DT]))--MAX('New Clients'[Calendar Date]))--LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today()) - 2returnCALCULATE(    SUM('New Clients'[Financial Customer Point Value]),    DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'Previous',    DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR] = prev2wknbr)

measures.name: 4 Wk Avg

measures.name: CY PW1 v 4Wk Avg
measures.expression: DIVIDE(([CY PW1 (Full Wk) New Clients]-[4 Wk Avg]),ABS([4 Wk Avg]),blank())

measures.name: 13 Wk Total Week Index
measures.expression: Var max_week = CALCULATE(    MAX('New Clients'[WeekIndex]) -1 )VAR start_week = max_week -12RETURNCALCULATE(              SUM('New Clients'[Financial Customer Point Value]),               FILTER('New Clients',               'New Clients'[WeekIndex] >= start_week              && 'New Clients'[WeekIndex] <= max_week))

measures.name: 13 Wk Avg

measures.name: CY PW1 v 13Wk Avg
measures.expression: DIVIDE(([CY PW1 (Full Wk) New Clients]-[13 Wk Avg]),ABS([13 Wk Avg]),blank())

measures.name: 52 Wk Total Week Index

measures.name: 52 Wk Avg

measures.name: CY PW1 v 52Wk Avg
measures.expression: DIVIDE(([CY PW1 (Full Wk) New Clients]-[52 Wk Avg]),ABS([52 Wk Avg]),blank())

measures.name: YTD New Clients - Trends tabs
measures.expression: var cy_start = CALCULATE(MIN('New Clients'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('New Clients','New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),'New Clients'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Current')var prev2wknbr = 52--LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today()) - 2RETURNCALCULATE(    SUM('New Clients'[Financial Customer Point Value]),    'New Clients'[Calendar Date] >= cy_start,    'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR] <= prev2wknbr)

measures.name: PYTD New Clients - Trends tabs

measures.name: YOY Change - Trends tabs

let    Source = DB2.Database('podwh021:50000', 'podwh021', [HierarchicalNavigation=true, Implementation='Microsoft', Query='SELECT DISTINCT#(lf)t1.ORZN_DEPT_CDE as RFO_CDE,#(lf)--t1.ORZN_ZONE_CDE as RFO_ZONE_NM,#(lf)t1.ORZN_SUB_DEPT_CDE as MVP_ID,#(lf)--(SUBSTRING(t1.ORZN_ZONE_CDE,6,5)) AS Market_ID,#(lf)t3.ORZN_DEPT_DSCR,#(lf)t3.EMP_ID,#(lf)t3.EMP_STS_TYP_CDE,#(lf)t3.trmn_dt,#(lf)t3.JOB_TYP_CDE,#(lf)t3.JOB_TYP_DSCR,#(lf)t3.EMP_NM,#(lf)case when t3.emp_nm is null then 'Vacant' Else t3.emp_nm end as market_leaders#(lf)FROM SEMANTIC.SALES_HIERARCHY_DIMENSION t1#(lf)left join#(lf)(#(lf)SELECT DISTINCT#(lf)T1.SALE_HIER_ID,#(lf)t1.orzn_zone_cde,#(lf)t1.orzn_dept_dscr,#(lf)t1.orzn_sub_dept_cde,#(lf)t2.orzn_dept_cde,#(lf)t2.EMP_ID,#(lf)t2.EMP_STS_TYP_CDE,#(lf)t2.trmn_dt,#(lf)t2.JOB_TYP_CDE,#(lf)t2.JOB_TYP_DSCR,#(lf)t2.EMP_NM#(lf)FROM#(lf)SEMANTIC.SALES_HIERARCHY_DIMENSION t1#(lf)left JOIN HUMAN_RESOURCES.CNF_EMP_DIM_DTL_CURR_CFDL t2 ON T1.SALE_HIER_ID = T2.emp_id#(lf)where t1.CURR_ROW_IND = 'Y'#(lf)and t2.emp_sts_typ_cde in ('A')#(lf)and t1.EFF_END_TMSP is null#(lf)AND T2.CURR_ROW_IND = 'Y'#(lf)and t1.EFF_END_TMSP is null#(lf)and t2.JOB_TYP_CDE IN ('001001')#(lf))#(lf)t3#(lf)on t1.orzn_sub_dept_cde = t3.orzn_sub_dept_cde#(lf)where t1.CURR_ROW_IND = 'Y'#(lf)and t1.eff_end_tmsp is null#(lf)--and t1.rfo_zone_sts_cde in ('A')#(lf)--and t3.EMP_STS_TYP_CDE = 'A'#(lf)--and substring(t1.orzn_zone_cde,6,2) <> '00'#(lf)and t1.orzn_zone_cde <> 'UKWN'#(lf)order BY t1.ORZN_SUB_DEPT_CDE;#(lf)']),    #'Filtered Rows' = Table.SelectRows(Source, each ([RFO_CDE] = '0001      ' or [RFO_CDE] = '0115      ' or [RFO_CDE] = '0190      ' or [RFO_CDE] = '0283      ' or [RFO_CDE] = '0291      ' or [RFO_CDE] = '0361      ' or [RFO_CDE] = '0383      ' or [RFO_CDE] = '0384      ' or [RFO_CDE] = '0435      ' or [RFO_CDE] = '0525      ' or [RFO_CDE] = '0716      ') and ([MVP_ID] <> '          ' and [MVP_ID] <> '0529-00   '))in    #'Filtered Rows'

columns.name: Cal_PYTD_Flag

columns.name: Cal_YTD_Flag
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Sunday], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'CURRENT'), True, False)

columns.name: PYTD Flag
columns.expression: var prevweeknum = LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Sunday]))return if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR] <= prevweeknum, DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='PREVIOUS'), True, False)

columns.name: Relative Year_Quarter
columns.expression: if(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year Flag]=TRUE(),'CY '& DTRB_PERF_DATES[Quarter_Q Count],if(AND(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_Flag]=TRUE(), AND(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Quarter]=QUARTER(TODAY()),DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_PYTD_Flag]=TRUE())), 'PY Current Quarter',if(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_Flag]=TRUE(), 'PY ' & DTRB_PERF_DATES[Quarter_Q Count],if(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_2_Flag]=TRUE(), 'PY2 ' & DTRB_PERF_DATES[Quarter_Q Count]))))

measures.name: Current Date
measures.expression: LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_DAY_TXT],'CURRENT')

measures.name: Current Year
measures.expression: LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT],'CURRENT')

measures.name: Prior Year
measures.expression: DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year] - 1

measures.name: PYTD DATE
measures.expression: (LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_END_DT], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today() -5 )) - 364

measures.name: Prior Year 2

measures.name: Current Year Max Week
measures.expression: CALCULATE(MAX(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR]), DTRB_PERF_DATES[YTD Flag]=TRUE())

source.expression: let    Source = DB2.Database('podwh021:50000', 'podwh021', [HierarchicalNavigation=true, Implementation='Microsoft']),    COMMON = Source{[Schema='COMMON']}[Data],    DTRB_PERF_DATES1 = COMMON{[Name='DTRB_PERF_DATES']}[Data]in    DTRB_PERF_DATES1

columns.name: WEEK TOTALS
columns.expression: CALCULATE(              SUM(ANBP_OTHERREV_SD[Value]),               FILTER(ANBP_OTHERREV_SD,               ANBP_OTHERREV_SD[ANBP_OtherRev]='ANBP' &&               ANBP_OTHERREV_SD[WeekIndex]>=135              && ANBP_OTHERREV_SD[WeekIndex]<=138 ))

measures.name: ANBP YOY Change

measures.name: CY ANBP

measures.name: ANBP PY

measures.name: ANBP PYTD

let    Source = DB2.Database('podwh021:50000', 'podwh021', [HierarchicalNavigation=true, Implementation='Microsoft', Query='SELECT DISTINCT#(lf)t1.ORZN_DEPT_CDE as RFO_CDE,#(lf)--t1.ORZN_ZONE_CDE as RFO_ZONE_NM,#(lf)t1.ORZN_SUB_DEPT_CDE as MVP_ID,#(lf)--(SUBSTRING(t1.ORZN_ZONE_CDE,6,5)) AS Market_ID,#(lf)t3.ORZN_DEPT_DSCR,#(lf)t3.EMP_ID,#(lf)t3.EMP_STS_TYP_CDE,#(lf)t3.trmn_dt,#(lf)t3.JOB_TYP_CDE,#(lf)t3.JOB_TYP_DSCR,#(lf)t3.EMP_NM,#(lf)t3.PEFR_FULL_NM,#(lf)case when t3.pefr_full_nm is null then 'Vacant' Else t3.pefr_full_nm end as market_leaders#(lf)FROM SEMANTIC.SALES_HIERARCHY_DIMENSION t1#(lf)left join#(lf)(#(lf)SELECT DISTINCT#(lf)T1.SALE_HIER_ID,#(lf)t1.orzn_zone_cde,#(lf)t1.orzn_dept_dscr,#(lf)t1.orzn_sub_dept_cde,#(lf)t2.orzn_dept_cde,#(lf)t2.EMP_ID,#(lf)t2.EMP_STS_TYP_CDE,#(lf)t2.trmn_dt,#(lf)t2.JOB_TYP_CDE,#(lf)t2.JOB_TYP_DSCR,#(lf)t2.EMP_NM,#(lf)t2.PEFR_FULL_NM#(lf)FROM#(lf)SEMANTIC.SALES_HIERARCHY_DIMENSION t1#(lf)left JOIN HUMAN_RESOURCES.CNF_EMP_DIM_DTL_CURR_CFDL t2 ON T1.SALE_HIER_ID = T2.emp_id#(lf)where t1.CURR_ROW_IND = 'Y' #(lf)and t2.emp_sts_typ_cde in ('A')#(lf)and t1.EFF_END_TMSP is null#(lf)AND T2.CURR_ROW_IND = 'Y'#(lf)and t1.EFF_END_TMSP is null#(lf)and t1.orzn_dept_cde IN ('0001','0714', '0716','0361', '0435','0283', '0291', '0525', '0115', '0190', '0384')#(lf)and t2.JOB_TYP_CDE IN ('001001')#(lf)#(lf))#(lf)t3#(lf)on t1.orzn_sub_dept_cde = t3.orzn_sub_dept_cde#(lf)where t1.CURR_ROW_IND = 'Y'#(lf)and t1.eff_end_tmsp is null#(lf)--and t1.rfo_zone_sts_cde in ('A')#(lf)--and t3.EMP_STS_TYP_CDE = 'A'#(lf)--and substring(t1.orzn_zone_cde,6,2) <> '00'#(lf)and t1.orzn_zone_cde <> 'UKWN'#(lf)and t1.orzn_dept_cde IN ('0001','0714', '0716','0361', '0435','0283', '0291', '0525', '0115', '0190', '0384')#(lf)#(lf)order BY t1.ORZN_SUB_DEPT_CDE;']),    #'Filtered Rows' = Table.SelectRows(Source, each ([MVP_ID] <> '          '))in    #'Filtered Rows'

measures.name: PY Business Day Count

measures.name: CY Business Day Count

All other weeks had 5 business days.','')

measures.expression: VAR CurrentDate= DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Date]Var PriorWeek= CALCULATE(SUM('Life Illustration Data CY'[Count]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_NBR]=WEEKNUM(CurrentDate)-3)Var PreviousWeek=CALCULATE (SUM('Life Illustration Data CY'[Count]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_NBR]=WeekNUM(CurrentDate)-2)RETURN(DIVIDE (PreviousWeek,PriorWeek))-1

measures.expression: VAR CurrentDate= DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Date]Var PW2= CALCULATE(SUM('Life Illustration Data CY'[Count]),WEEKNUM('Life Illustration Data CY'[Day])=WEEKNUM(CurrentDate)-2,YEAR('Life Illustration Data CY'[Day])=Year(CurrentDate))Returnif (ISFILTERED(RFO_Market[Advisor Group])=TRUE,Blank(),if (ISFILTERED('Tenure Group Bridge Table'[Tenure Group]),BLANK(),If(PW2=BLANK(),'-',Divide([PW Illustration2],[PW2 Illustration])-1)))

columns.name: YTD Flag two Sundays
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[Two Sundays Ago], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_NBR] = DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year]), True, False)

columns.name: PYTD Flag
columns.expression: var prevweeknum = LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Sunday]))return if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR] <= prevweeknum, DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='PREVIOUS'), True, False)

measures.name: Current Year
measures.expression: year(today()-5)

measures.name: Prior Year 2
measures.expression: DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year] - 2

measures.name: Markets Filter
measures.expression: IF(    MAX('Market Parameter - Capacity'[Capacity Market View])='Experienced Advisor Markets'    && MAX(WMFC_CD[Experienced Advisor Markets]) IN {'PMC (59)','GPA (69)','GPD (79)'},    1,    0)

measures.name: Markets Filter v2
measures.expression: IF(    MAX('Market Parameter - Capacity'[Capacity Market View])='Experienced Advisor Markets'    && MAX(WMFC_CD[PG COE Markets]) = {'PG COE Engaged Markets (59,69,79)'},    1,    0)

measures.name: Markets Filter v3
measures.expression: IF(    MAX('Market Parameter - Capacity'[Capacity Market View])='Experienced Advisor Markets'    && MAX(WMFC_CD[Market]) IN {'59','69','79'},    1,    0)

columns.name: Level 3 Product Line Of Business Code
Level 3 Product Line Of Business Description
PYTD NFC Flag
columns.expression: if(and('NFC'[Calendar Date] <= DATE(YEAR(today())-1,MONTH(today()),DAY(today())), 'NFC'[Distribution Performance Reporting Year Number] = YEAR(today())-1), 1, 0)

columns.name: PY2TD NFC Flag

columns.name: PY2 NFC Flag
columns.expression: var py_start = CALCULATE(MIN('NFC'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('NFC','NFC'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),all('NFC'),'NFC'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Previous') var py_end = CALCULATE(MAX('NFC'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('NFC','NFC'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),all('NFC'),'NFC'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Previous') var py2_start= date(year(py_start)-1,month(py_start),day(py_start)) var py2_end= date(year(py_end)-1,month(py_end),day(py_end)) var flagind = if('NFC'[Calendar Date] <= py2_end && 'NFC'[Calendar Date] >= py2_start,1, 0)Returnflagind

measures.name: PY New Clients
measures.expression: --var _total=CALCULATE(sum('NFC'[Financial Customer Point Value]), 'NFC'[PY NFC Flag] = 1)--var _total=CALCULATE(sum('NFC'[Financial Customer Point Value]),'NFC'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Previous')--RETURN--if(isblank(_total),0,_total)--Updated 1/26/2022var min_date = min(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT])var max_date = Max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT])var _total = calculate(sum('NFC'[Financial Customer Point Value]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] >= (min_date-365),DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= (max('DTRB_PERF_DATES'[End of Year Date])-365))Returnif(isblank(_total),0,_total)

measures.name: PY2 New Clients
measures.expression: var _total=CALCULATE(sum('NFC'[Financial Customer Point Value]), 'NFC'[PY2 NFC Flag] = 1)RETURNif(isblank(_total),0,_total)

measures.name: PY2TD New Clients
measures.expression: var cy_start = CALCULATE(MIN('NFC'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('NFC','NFC'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),all('NFC'),'NFC'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Current')var cy_end = CALCULATE(MAX('NFC'[Calendar Date]),ALLEXCEPT('NFC','NFC'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]),all('NFC'),'NFC'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Current')var py2_start = date(YEAR(cy_start)-2,MONTH(cy_start),DAY(cy_start))var py2_end = DATE(YEAR(cy_end)-2,MONTH(cy_end),DAY(cy_end))var _total = CALCULATE(SUM('NFC'[Financial Customer Point Value]), 'NFC', 'NFC'[Calendar Date] <= py2_end && 'NFC'[Calendar Date] >= py2_start)RETURNif(isblank(_total),0,_total)

measures.name: PYTD New Clients
measures.expression: --var _total=CALCULATE(sum('NFC'[Financial Customer Point Value]), 'NFC'[PYTD NFC Flag] = 1)--var _total=CALCULATE(sum('NFC'[Financial Customer Point Value]), 'NFC'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='Previous')--RETURN--if(isblank(_total),0,_total)--Updated 1/26/2022var min_date = min(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]) var max_date = Max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT])var _total = calculate(sum('NFC'[Financial Customer Point Value]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] >= (min_date-365),DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= (max_date-365))Returnif(isblank(_total),0,_total)

measures.name: YOY Change
measures.expression: VAR __BASELINE_VALUE = [PYTD New Clients]  VAR __VALUE_TO_COMPARE = [YTD New Clients]  var _total =    IF(        NOT ISBLANK(__VALUE_TO_COMPARE),        DIVIDE(__VALUE_TO_COMPARE - __BASELINE_VALUE, __BASELINE_VALUE)    )Returnif(isblank(_total),0,_total)

measures.name: Total New Money

columns.name: Current Pace Target
columns.expression: if('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Process Date]=date(2023,12,31),calculate(sum('Pace Performance Snapshot'[EOY Pace Target])),if('Pace Performance Snapshot'[TSID] in {'TS78250','TS75194','TS77919'},calculate(sum('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Target AMT])+((sum('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Tenure_Months])-sum('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Month]))*sum('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Target Range]))),    calculate(sum('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Pace_Target]))))

measures.name: Above Count
measures.expression: var MAXDATE = max('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Process Date])returncalculate(    distinctcount('Pace Performance Snapshot'[TSID]),    filter('Pace Performance Snapshot','Pace Performance Snapshot'[ABOVE/BELOW]='ABOVE'),    'Pace Performance Snapshot'[Process Date]= MAXDATE)

measures.name: Below Count

measures.name: % Above Pace
measures.expression: divide('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Above Count],'Pace Performance Snapshot'[Above Count]+[Below Count])

measures.name: Current GAP to Target

measures.name: EOY Target

measures.expression: calculate(sum('Pace Performance Snapshot'[GRID Credit Amount])+sum(RFO_PENDING_DETAIL[EstimatedSalesCreditAmt])-'Grid Revenue'[Grid Revenue Falling Off EOM]-'Pace Performance Snapshot'[EOM Target],'Pace Performance Snapshot'[ABOVE_BELOW]<>'')

measures.name: Historical Above Count
measures.expression: calculate(    count('Pace Performance Snapshot'[TSID]),    filter('Pace Performance Snapshot','Pace Performance Snapshot'[ABOVE/BELOW]='ABOVE'))

measures.name: Historical Below Count
measures.expression: calculate(    count('Pace Performance Snapshot'[TSID]),    filter('Pace Performance Snapshot','Pace Performance Snapshot'[ABOVE/BELOW]='BELOW'))

measures.name: Historical % Above Pace
measures.expression: if(ISBLANK([Historical Above Count])&& NOT(ISBLANK([NFA Count])),0,divide('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Historical Above Count],'Pace Performance Snapshot'[Historical Above Count]+[Historical Below Count]))

measures.name: Current_Pace_Target
measures.expression: var MAXDATE = max('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Process Date])returncalculate(sum('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Current Pace Target]),'Pace Performance Snapshot'[Process Date]=MAXDATE)

measures.name: ABOVE/BELOW
measures.expression: Var Pace_Amt = 'Pace Performance Snapshot'[Pace Amount]Var Pace_Tgt = 'Pace Performance Snapshot'[Current_Pace_Target]Var Diff = Pace_Amt - Pace_TgtReturnIF(FORMAT('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Current GAP to Target],'Whole Number') <> '',   IF(Diff > 0, 'ABOVE', 'BELOW'),   BLANK())

measures.name: ABOVE/BELOW LH
measures.expression: Var Pace_Amt = 'Pace Performance Snapshot'[LH Pace Amount]Var Pace_Tgt = 'Pace Performance Snapshot'[LH Pace Target]Var Diff = Pace_Amt - Pace_TgtReturnIF(FORMAT('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Current GAP to LH Target],'Whole Number') <> '',   IF(Diff > 0, 'ABOVE', 'BELOW'),   BLANK())

measures.name: Tonnage %
measures.expression: divide([Pace Amount],sum('Pace Performance Snapshot'[Current Pace Target]))

Compensation Level 5 Product Line Of Business Subgroup Code

measures.name: Grid Revenue Falling Off
measures.expression: calculate(sum('Grid Revenue'[Grid Credit Amount]),'Grid Revenue'[Rolling Off FLAG]='Y','Pace Performance Snapshot'[Tenure_Months]>=12)

measures.name: Grid Revenue Falling Off EOY
measures.expression: var mindate = DATE(Year(today())-1,Month(today()),day(today()-1))var maxdate = DATE(Year(today())-1,12,31)returncalculate(sum('Grid Revenue'[Grid Credit Amount]),'Grid Revenue'[Calendar Day Date]>=mindate,'Grid Revenue'[Calendar Day Date]<=maxdate,'Pace Performance Snapshot'[Tenure_Months]>=12)

measures.name: Grid Revenue Falling Off EOQ

measures.name: Grid Revenue Falling Off EOM

D.CUST_LGAL_FMT_NM,#(lf)       D.CUST_GRP_ID_NBR,#(lf)       E.STP_STS_CDE,#(lf)       case when E.fut_vlu_indx_cde = 'GOLD' then 'Gold'#(lf)            when E.fut_vlu_indx_cde = 'SILVR' then D.clas_cust_rpt_cde = 'NAOWN' then 'Non-Member'#(lf)#(tab)    when a.mbr_typ_cde = 'NON' and D.clas_cust_rpt_cde <> 'NAOWN' then 'Prospect'#(lf)       end as MBRTYPE,#(lf)       B.EMP_ORZN_ID#(lf) AND#(lf)       A.MBR_TYP_CDE IN ('BEN','NON','ASSOC','JUV') AND#(lf)       B.EMP_ORZN_ID LIKE 'TS%' inner join#(lf)       MEMBER.CNF_CUSTOMER_DIM_CFDL C#(lf)    ON B.CUST_ID_NBR = C.CUST_ID_NBR Table.AddColumn(#'Filtered Rows1', 'Client Service Model', each if [FUTUREVALUE] = 'Gold' and [STP_STS_CDE] = 'YES' then 'A'else if [FUTUREVALUE] = 'Silver' and [STP_STS_CDE] = 'YES' then 'B'else if [FUTUREVALUE] = 'Gold' and [STP_STS_CDE] <> 'YES' then 'B'else if [FUTUREVALUE] = 'Bronze' and [STP_STS_CDE] = 'YES' then 'C'else if [FUTUREVALUE] = 'Silver' and [STP_STS_CDE] <> 'YES' then 'C'else if measures.name: YTD Grid Revenue
measures.expression: var min_date = min(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT])  Var max_date = Max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT])  var _gridtotal = calculate(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] >= min_date,DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= max_date)  var _gridtotal_team = calculate(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]), 'Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[TeamSale_Ind] = 'Y',                         DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] >= min_date,DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= max_date) ReturnIF([TeamNmFiltered] = 1, IF(ISBLANK(_gridtotal_team),0,_gridtotal_team), IF(ISBLANK(_gridtotal),0,_gridtotal))

measures.name: Best Day Amount Grid Revenue
measures.expression: var gcamt_ind = MAXX(VALUES(Grid_Rev_Snowflake[Calendar Day Date]),[YTD Grid Revenue])  return  IF(ISBLANK(gcamt_ind),0,gcamt_ind)

measures.name: Best Date Grid Revenue
measures.expression: CALCULATE(MAX('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Calendar Day Date]),FILTER('Grid_Rev_Snowflake', [Grid Credit Amount]=MAX(Grid_Rev_Snowflake[Grid Credit Amount])))

measures.name: MTD Grid Revenue
measures.expression: var _gridtotal = CALCULATE(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]),DATESMTD(Grid_Rev_Snowflake[Calendar Day Date]))  var _gridtotal_team = calculate(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]), 'Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[TeamSale_Ind] = 'Y', DATESMTD(Grid_Rev_Snowflake[Calendar Day Date]))  returnIF([TeamNmFiltered] = 1, IF(ISBLANK(_gridtotal_team),0,_gridtotal_team), IF(ISBLANK(_gridtotal),0,_gridtotal))

measures.name: WTD Grid Revenue
measures.expression: var _gridtotal = CALCULATE(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]), 'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_TXT]='CURRENT')  var _gridtotal_team = calculate(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]), 'Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[TeamSale_Ind] = 'Y',                        'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_TXT]='CURRENT') ReturnIF([TeamNmFiltered] = 1, IF(ISBLANK(_gridtotal_team),0,_gridtotal_team), IF(ISBLANK(_gridtotal),0,_gridtotal))

measures.name: Previous Day Grid Revenue
measures.expression: var _gridtotal = CALCULATE(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]), 'Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Calendar Day Date] = (today()-1))  var _gridtotal_team = calculate(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]), 'Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[TeamSale_Ind] = 'Y',                        'Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Calendar Day Date] = (today()-1)) ReturnIF([TeamNmFiltered] = 1, IF(ISBLANK(_gridtotal_team),0,_gridtotal_team), IF(ISBLANK(_gridtotal),0,_gridtotal))

measures.name: PYTD Grid Revenue
measures.expression: var min_date = min(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT])  Var max_date = Max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT])   var _gridtotal = calculate(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] >= (min_date-365),DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= (max_date-365))  var _gridtotal_team = calculate(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]), 'Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[TeamSale_Ind] = 'Y',                         DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] >= (min_date-365),DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= (max_date-365)) ReturnIF([TeamNmFiltered] = 1, IF(ISBLANK(_gridtotal_team),0,_gridtotal_team), IF(ISBLANK(_gridtotal),0,_gridtotal))

measures.name: Advancer/Decliner
measures.expression: if([YTD Grid Revenue]>[PYTD Grid Revenue],1,0)

measures.name: Advancer Grid Revnue YTD
measures.expression: Calculate([YTD Grid Revenue],filter(Producer_Snowflake, Grid_Rev_Snowflake[Advancer/Decliner]=1))

measures.name: Decliner Grid Revnue YTD
measures.expression: Calculate([YTD Grid Revenue],filter(Producer_Snowflake, Grid_Rev_Snowflake[Advancer/Decliner]=0))

measures.name: Advancer Count
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    DISTINCTCOUNT(Producer_Snowflake[EMP_ID]),    filter(Producer_Snowflake,    [Advancer/Decliner]=1))

measures.name: Decliner Count
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    DISTINCTCOUNT(Producer_Snowflake[EMP_ID]),    filter(Producer_Snowflake,    [Advancer/Decliner]=0))

measures.name: YOY Grid
measures.expression: var min_date = min(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT])  Var max_date = Max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT])  var _ytd_total = calculate(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] >= min_date,DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= max_date)  var _pytd_total = calculate(sum('Grid_Rev_Snowflake'[Grid Credit Amount]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] >= (min_date-365),DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= (max_date-365))ReturnIF((_pytd_total) = 0,0, ((_ytd_total - _pytd_total) / _pytd_total))

let    Source = Sql.Database('DBRESONANTPRD', 'Resonant', [Query='SELECT DISTINCT RTRIM(LTRIM(Replace(A.PolNumber,'?',''))) as BenefitContractNumber,#(lf)     A.CommissionablePremiumAmt as COMM_PREM_AMT,#(lf)     A.BASECOVERAGE_ID, #(lf)     B.ProductCode as Res_ProductCode #(lf)  FROM Resonant.dbo.life_lifepolicy #(lf)  A LEFT JOIN#(lf)     Resonant.dbo.life_coverage B #(lf)        ON (A.BaseCoverage_ID = B.ID)#(lf)  WHERE A.CommissionablePremiumAmt > 0'])in    Source

let    Source = Table.NestedJoin(RES_DATA, {'Res_ProductCode'}, NSC_RATES, {'PRODUCT'}, 'NSC_RATES', JoinKind.LeftOuter),    #'Expanded NSC_RATES' = Table.ExpandTableColumn(Source, 'NSC_RATES', {'PRODUCT', 'AGE_LOW', 'AGE_HIGH', 'COMM_RATE', 'NSC_RATE', 'POLICY_FEE'}, {'NSC_RATES.PRODUCT', 'NSC_RATES.AGE_LOW', 'NSC_RATES.AGE_HIGH', 'NSC_RATES.COMM_RATE', 'NSC_RATES.NSC_RATE', 'NSC_RATES.POLICY_FEE'}),    #'Filtered Rows' = Table.SelectRows(#'Expanded NSC_RATES', each [BenefitContractNumber] <> null and [BenefitContractNumber] <> ''),    #'Removed Duplicates' = Table.Distinct(#'Filtered Rows', {'BenefitContractNumber'}),    #'Filtered Rows1' = Table.SelectRows(#'Removed Duplicates', each ([NSC_RATES.PRODUCT] = 'LTIV10YR' or [NSC_RATES.PRODUCT] = 'LTIV15YR' or [NSC_RATES.PRODUCT] = 'LTIV20YR' or [NSC_RATES.PRODUCT] = 'LTIV30YR'))in    #'Filtered Rows1'

let    Source = DB2.Database('PODWH021:50000', 'PODWH021', [HierarchicalNavigation=true, Implementation='Microsoft', Query='SELECT DISTINCT t1.ORZN_DEPT_CDE AS RFO, #(lf)          /* TAG_MVP_Mkt */#(lf)          t1.ORZN_ZONE_CDE AS TAG_MVP_Mkt,/* MVP_ID */#(lf)      SUBSTRING(t1.ORZN_ZONE_CDE,1,7) AS MVP_ID,/* Zone_ID */#(lf)          RIGHT(RTRIM(t1.ORZN_ZONE_CDE),2) AS Zone_ID,#(lf)         t1.SALE_HIER_ID AS TSID, #(lf)          /* Strt_Dt */#(lf)          t1.EFF_BEG_TMSP,#(lf)          /* END_DATE */#(lf)          (CASE WHEN t1.EFF_END_TMSP is null #(lf)             THEN '12-31-9999'#(lf)               ELSE t1.EFF_END_TMSP-1#(lf)          END)AS EFF_END_TMSP#(lf)      FROM SEMANTIC.SALES_HIERARCHY_DIMENSION t1#(lf)      WHERE SUBSTRING(t1.SALE_HIER_ID,1,2) in ('DP','TS') #(lf)        AND t1.CURR_ROW_IND = 'Y' #(lf)        AND ( t1.EFF_END_TMSP > t1.EFF_BEG_TMSP OR t1.EFF_END_TMSP IS null )']),    #'Changed Type' = Table.TransformColumnTypes(Source,{{'EFF_BEG_TMSP', type date}, {'EFF_END_TMSP', type date}}),    #'Duplicated Column' = Table.DuplicateColumn(#'Changed Type', 'TSID', 'TSID - Copy'),    #'Renamed Columns' = Table.RenameColumns(#'Duplicated Column',{{'TSID - Copy', 'TSID_trimmed'}}),    #'Trimmed Text' = Table.TransformColumns(#'Renamed Columns',{{'TSID_trimmed', Text.Trim, type text}, {'RFO', Text.Trim, type text}, {'ZONE_ID', Text.Trim, type text}})in    #'Trimmed Text'

columns.name: Week_Index
columns.expression: Var year_num = (YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])-YEAR(MIN(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])))+1var year_diff = (YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])-YEAR(MIN(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])))Var week_num = WEEKNUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])RETURN(year_diff*52)+week_num

columns.name: Region
columns.expression: SWITCH(  TRUE,  ISBLANK('RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG]),  '(Blank)',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0810'},  'Colorado Springs',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0361',    '0365',    '0435',    '0496'},  'Established',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0165',    '0240',    '0283',    '0291',    '0410',    '0525'},  'Growth',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0115',    '0190',    '0384',    '0475',    '0529'},  'Invest',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0716'},  'TAN',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0383'},  'TFGT',  'Other')

columns.name: Division
columns.expression: SWITCH(  TRUE,  ISBLANK('RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG]),  '(Blank)',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0283',    '0365',    '0435',    '0496',    '0810'},  'Central',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0115',    '0165',    '0190',    '0240',    '0361',    '0384'},  'East',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0716'},  'TAN',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0383'},  'TFGT',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0291',    '0410',    '0475',    '0525',    '0529'},  'West',  'Other')

columns.expression: SWITCH(  TRUE,  ISBLANK('RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG]),  '(Blank)',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0716'},  'TAN',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0001',    '0115',    '0190',    '0283',    '0291',    '0361',    '0384',    '0435',    '0525'},  'Thrivent Advisor Group',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[TAG] IN {'0383'},  'Virtual Advice',  'Other')

columns.name: Contract Max Week
columns.expression: VAR ContractMaxWeek = CALCULATE(        MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),        ALLEXCEPT(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Benefit Contract Number])    )    VAR MaxYear = YEAR(CALCULATE(            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))RETURNIF((RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]=ContractMaxWeek) && YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])=MaxYear,'Contract MaxWeek','Not Contract MaxWeek')

columns.name: Contract Status Summary
columns.expression: SWITCH(  TRUE,  ISBLANK('RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[Contract MaxWeek Status]),  '(Blank)',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[Contract MaxWeek Status] IN {'Cancelled'},  'Cancelled',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[Contract MaxWeek Status] IN {'Declined'},  'Declined',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[Contract MaxWeek Status] IN {'Issued'},  'Issued',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[Contract MaxWeek Status] IN {'Pending',    'Received'},  'Pending',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[Contract MaxWeek Status] IN {'Retired'},  'Retired',  'RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE'[Contract MaxWeek Status])

columns.name: Contract Min Week
columns.expression: VAR ContractMinWeek = CALCULATE(        MIN(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),        ALLEXCEPT(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Benefit Contract Number])    )    VAR MaxYear = YEAR(CALCULATE(            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))RETURNIF((RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]=ContractMinWeek) && YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])=MaxYear,1,0)

columns.name: Pending Dropped Record
columns.expression: if(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Contract Status Summary]='Pending' && RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Pend CW_Flag]='No','Dropped Record',RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Contract Status Summary])

columns.name: Contract Max_Week
columns.expression: VAR ContractMaxWeek = CALCULATE(        MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),        ALLEXCEPT(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Benefit Contract Number])    )    VAR MaxYear = YEAR(CALCULATE(            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))RETURNIF((RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]=ContractMaxWeek) && YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])=MaxYear,1,0)

columns.name: Contract Max Week any year
columns.expression: VAR ContractMaxWeek = CALCULATE(        MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),        ALLEXCEPT(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Benefit Contract Number])    )   RETURNIF((RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]=ContractMaxWeek),'Contract MaxWeek','Not Contract MaxWeek')

columns.name: Contract Min Week any year
columns.expression: VAR ContractMinWeek = CALCULATE(        MIN(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),        ALLEXCEPT(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Benefit Contract Number])    )   RETURNIF((RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]=ContractMinWeek),'Contract MinWeek','Not Contract MinWeek')

measures.name: Received CW
measures.expression: //VAR MaxWeek = WEEKNUM(CALCULATE(//            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))//VAR MaxYear = YEAR(CALCULATE(//            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))//RETURN//    CALCULATE(//        SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),//            FILTER(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,WEEKNUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])=MaxWeek && YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])=MaxYear))+0//            ANBP PW = // var PreWk = LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today()) - 2Var max_week = CALCULATE(    MAX(DTRB_PERF_DATES[WeekIndex]),    FILTER(DTRB_PERF_DATES, DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]=(TODAY())))-1Var MaxDay= CALCULATE(MAX(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]),FILTER(DTRB_PERF_DATES,DTRB_PERF_DATES[WeekIndex]=max_week))VAR start_week = max_week VAR StartDay=CALCULATE(MIN(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]),FILTER(DTRB_PERF_DATES,DTRB_PERF_DATES[WeekIndex]=start_week))returnCALCULATE(SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),  RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date]<= MaxDay,RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date]>=StartDay)

measures.name: Received YTD
measures.expression: //VAR MaxYear = YEAR(CALCULATE(//            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))//RETURN//CALCULATE(//   SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),//    FILTER((RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE),//        YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Transaction Receive Date])=MaxYear))+0CALCULATE(   SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),   DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_YTD_Flag]={TRUE()},RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Contract Min Week any year]='Contract MinWeek')

measures.name: Received PYTD
measures.expression: //var py = YEAR(CALCULATE(//            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))-1//var cw = WEEKNUM(CALCULATE(//            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE)))//RETURN//CALCULATE(//   SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),//    FILTER(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,//        YEAR(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])=py//        && WEEKNUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending])<=cw//    )//)+0CALCULATE(   SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),   DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_PYTD_Flag] in {TRUE},RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Contract Min Week any year]='Contract MinWeek')

measures.name: Pending Count CW
measures.expression: VAR MaxWeek = CALCULATE(            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE))RETURN    CALCULATE(        SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Pending]),            FILTER((RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE),RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week_Ending]=MaxWeek))+0

measures.name: Received 13 Wk Total Week_Index
measures.expression: VAR MaxWeek = CALCULATE(            MAX(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week Ending_Index]),ALL(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE))Var start_week = MaxWeek - 12RETURNCALCULATE(              SUM(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Received]),              FILTER(RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE,                 RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week Ending_Index]>= start_week                 && RECD_PEND_COMPL_ZBE[Week Ending_Index]<= MaxWeek))+0
