columns.name: Cal_PYTD_Flag
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[PYTD DATE], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'PREVIOUS'), True, False)

columns.name: Cal_YTD_Flag
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Sunday], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'CURRENT'), True, False)

columns.name: PYTD Flag
columns.expression: var prevweeknum = LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Sunday]))return if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR] <= prevweeknum, DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='PREVIOUS'), True, False)

measures.name: PYTD DATE
measures.expression: (LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_END_DT], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today() -5 )) - 364

measures.name: Current Year
measures.expression: LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT],'CURRENT')

measures.name: Current Date
measures.expression: today()

measures.name: Prior Year
measures.expression: DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year] - 1

measures.name: Prior Year 2
measures.expression: DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year] - 2

measures.name: Current Year Max Week
measures.expression: CALCULATE(MAX(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR]), DTRB_PERF_DATES[YTD Flag]=TRUE())

measures.name: YTD Life Vol
measures.expression: calculate(sum('Life Volumes'[LIFE_VOLUME_AMOUNT]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[YTD Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: YTD_LifeVol_Cummulative
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    [Life Vol Running Total],    DTRB_PERF_DATES[YTD Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: PY Life Vol
measures.expression: calculate(sum('Life Volumes'[LIFE_VOLUME_AMOUNT]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Year Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: PY Life Vol Running Total

measures.name: What's New Msg
measures.expression: VAR EndDate=LOOKUPVALUE('AdviceMessage'[End Date],'AdviceMessage'[Message Description],'What's New')RETURNIF(TODAY()<=EndDate,LOOKUPVALUE('AdviceMessage'[Message],'AdviceMessage'[Message Description], 'What's New'),'')

measures.name: Show What's New Msg Box
measures.expression: VAR EndDate=LOOKUPVALUE('AdviceMessage'[End Date],'AdviceMessage'[Message Description],'What's New')RETURNIF(TODAY()<=EndDate,1,0)

measures.name: Alert Msg
measures.expression: VAR AlertMsg=LOOKUPVALUE('AdviceMessage'[Message],'AdviceMessage'[Message Description],'Alert!')RETURNIF(AlertMsg<>BLANK(),AlertMsg, '')

measures.name: Show Alert Msg Box
measures.expression: VAR AlertMsg=LOOKUPVALUE('AdviceMessage'[Message],'AdviceMessage'[Message Description],'Alert!')RETURNIF(AlertMsg<>BLANK(),1,0)

columns.name: Adopted Client Households
columns.expression: var _total = Calculate(DISTINCTCOUNT(Client_HHLD[SF_HH_ID]),                        Client_HHLD[SF_HH_ID] <>  BLANK(), Client_HHLD[Client Description]= 'Client' ,                        Client_HHLD[Adoption CEO] = 1)Return  IF(ISBLANK(_total),0,_total)

columns.name: Adopted Households
columns.expression: var _total = Calculate(DISTINCTCOUNT(Client_HHLD[SF_HH_ID]),                        Client_HHLD[SF_HH_ID] <> BLANK(), Client_HHLD[Client Description]= 'Client' || Client_HHLD[Client Description] = 'New Client',                        Client_HHLD[Adoption] = 1)Return  IF(ISBLANK(_total),0,_total)

columns.name: Adopted New Client Households
columns.expression: var _total = Calculate(DISTINCTCOUNT(Client_HHLD[SF_HH_ID]),                        Client_HHLD[SF_HH_ID] <> BLANK(), Client_HHLD[Client Description] = 'New Client',                        Client_HHLD[Adoption CEO] = 1)Return  IF(ISBLANK(_total),0,_total)

columns.name: RULE FA
columns.expression: var _adoptHHLD = 'Producer_Snowflake'[Adopted Households] + 'Producer_Snowflake'[Advice Prorate]  var _rulechk = IF(_adoptHHLD >= 'Producer_Snowflake'[Advice Target], 'Y', 'N')RETURNIF(ISBLANK(_rulechk),'N',_rulechk)

columns.name: Advice Prorate
columns.expression: var _hireYear = 2024  var _hireMonth = If(year(RELATED('Attendance Data'[Class Month]))= _hireYear, month(related('Attendance Data'[Class Month])), 0)  var _foundations = 'Producer_Snowflake'[Foundations]    var _calc =     IF(_foundations = 1,       CALCULATE(Max('ProRate Dim'[Prorate]),       USERELATIONSHIP('DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Current Month],'ProRate Dim'[Month]), 'ProRate Dim'[Month] = _hireMonth),0)         RETURN _calc

columns.name: Advice Target
columns.expression: VAR CurrentMonthNumber= IF(MONTH(TODAY())=1,12,MONTH(TODAY()))VAR PreviousMonthNumber= IF(MONTH(TODAY())=1,12,MONTH(TODAY())-1) VAR MonthForGoal= IF(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current BD of the month]>2, CurrentMonthNumber, PreviousMonthNumber)return  CALCULATE(Max('ProRate Dim'[Target]), USERELATIONSHIP('DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Current Month],'ProRate Dim'[Month]), 'ProRate Dim'[Month] = MonthForGoal)

columns.name: RULE FA AIP
columns.expression: --No Prorate included in the calculation  var _adoptHHLD = 'Producer_Snowflake'[Adopted Households]  var _rulechk = IF(_adoptHHLD >= 'Producer_Snowflake'[Advice Target], 'Y', 'N')RETURNIF(ISBLANK(_rulechk),'N',_rulechk)

columns.name: Sierra Metric
columns.expression: IF(AND('Sr Market Directors'[Hires Count]>=4,'Sr Market Directors'[Hires Count]<6),1,-999999)+rankx('Sr Market Directors','Sr Market Directors'[Zone_Leader_Name])

columns.name: Sierra Rank
columns.expression: if('Sr Market Directors'[Sierra Metric]>0,rankx('Sr Market Directors','Sr Market Directors'[Sierra Metric]),-999999)

columns.name: Summitt Metric
columns.expression: IF(AND('Sr Market Directors'[Hires Count]>=6,'Sr Market Directors'[Hires Count]<1000),1,-999999)+rankx('Sr Market Directors','Sr Market Directors'[Zone_Leader_Name])

columns.name: Summitt Rank
columns.expression: if('Sr Market Directors'[Summitt Metric]>0,rankx('Sr Market Directors','Sr Market Directors'[Summitt Metric]),-999999)

columns.name: Hires Rank
columns.expression: Round(Rankx('Sr Market Directors','Sr Market Directors'[Hires Count]),0)

columns.name: Retention Rank
columns.expression: Round(Rankx('Sr Market Directors','Sr Market Directors'[Retention Rate]),0)

columns.name: Advice Rank
columns.expression: Round(Rankx('Sr Market Directors','Sr Market Directors'[Advice Adoption.Adopting Advisors %]),0)

columns.name: Pace Rank
columns.expression: Var PRank = Round(Rankx('Sr Market Directors','Sr Market Directors'[Above FA Count]),0) Return Blank()

columns.name: Total Rank
columns.expression: var TRank = ROUND(0.25 * 'Sr Market Directors'[Hires Rank] + 0.25 * 'Sr Market Directors'[Retention Rank]  + 0.4 * 'Sr Market Directors'[Pace Rank] + 0.1 * 'Sr Market Directors'[Advice Rank],1)ReturnBlank()

columns.name: Rank Rank
columns.expression: var RRank = Round(Rankx('Sr Market Directors','Sr Market Directors'[Total Rank],,ASC),0)ReturnBlank()

measures.name: Leader JFW YTD Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide('Appointments/PC/JFW'[YTD Leader JFW],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR])),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[YTD Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: Market JFW YTD Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide('Appointments/PC/JFW'[YTD Market JFW],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR])),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[YTD Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: NFP 4 Mo JFW Cov - L30
measures.expression: CALCULATE(          divide([YTD Market JFW FP],[YTD Appointments]),          'Appointments/PC/JFW'[FP Tenure - NFP 4 Mo] = 'NFP 4 Mo',          'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Prior 30 days Flag] in {TRUE},          'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000','002010','002022','002025','002026','002027','003100','003500'})

measures.name: NFP 4 Mo JFW Cov - N14
measures.expression: CALCULATE(          divide([N14 Market JFW],[N14 Appointments]),          'Appointments/PC/JFW'[FP Tenure - NFP 4 Mo] = 'NFP 4 Mo',          'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Next 14 days Flag] in {TRUE},          'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000','002010','002022','002025','002026','002027','003100','003500'})

measures.name: N14 Appointments
measures.expression: calculate(    DISTINCTCOUNT('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key]),    'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Worker Appointment Association] = 'Owner',    'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000','002010','002025','002026','002027','003100','003500'},    DTRB_PERF_DATES[Next 14 days Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: N14 Market JFW
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    DISTINCTCOUNT('Appointments/PC/JFW'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key]),    'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Worker Appointment Association] = 'Owner',    'Appointments/PC/JFW'[JFW_IND] = 1,    'Appointments/PC/JFW'[Historical Job Type Code] in {'002000','002010','002022','002025','002026','002027','003100','003500'},    DTRB_PERF_DATES[Next 14 days Flag] in {TRUE})

columns.name: PYTD Flag
columns.expression: var prevweeknum = LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Sunday]))return if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR] <= prevweeknum, DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT]='PREVIOUS'), True, False)

columns.name: Cal_YTD_Flag
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Sunday], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'CURRENT'), True, False)

columns.name: Cal_PYTD_Flag
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[PYTD DATE], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT] = 'PREVIOUS'), True, False)

columns.name: PYTD Flag two Sundays
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[PYTD DATE two Sundays], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_NBR] = DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Year]), True, False)

columns.name: YTD Flag two Sundays
columns.expression: if(and(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT] <= DTRB_PERF_DATES[Two Sundays Ago], DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_NBR] = DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year]), True, False)

measures.name: Current Date
measures.expression: today()

measures.name: Current Year
measures.expression: LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_TXT],'CURRENT')

measures.name: Prior YEar
measures.expression: DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year] - 1

measures.name: PYTD DATE
measures.expression: (LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_END_DT], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today() - 5)) - 364

measures.name: Prior Year 2
measures.expression: DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year] - 2

measures.name: PYTD DATE two Sundays
measures.expression: (LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_END_DT], DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT], today() - 379))

measures.name: Days into Year
measures.expression: CALCULATE(COUNT(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[YTD Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: Days in Year
measures.expression: CALCULATE(COUNT(DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: Weeks Remaining NFC
measures.expression: calculate(52-MAX(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[YTD Flag two Sundays] in {TRUE})

measures.name: Current Week Number
measures.expression: LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Week Flag],'TRUE')

source.expression: let    Source = DB2.Database('podwh021:50000', 'podwh021', [HierarchicalNavigation=true, Implementation='Microsoft']),    COMMON = Source{[Schema='COMMON']}[Data],    DTRB_PERF_DATES1 = COMMON{[Name='DTRB_PERF_DATES']}[Data]in    DTRB_PERF_DATES1

measures.name: YTD CP Plus
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    sum('CP _Plus'[CP+ Scores Above]),    DTRB_PERF_DATES[YTD Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: PYTD CP Plus
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    sum('CP _Plus'[CP+ Scores Above]),    DTRB_PERF_DATES[PYTD Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: PY CP PLus
measures.expression: CALCULATE(sum('CP _Plus'[CP+ Scores Above]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Year Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: YOY Change CP
measures.expression: DIVIDE(('CP _Plus'[YTD CP Plus] - 'CP _Plus'[PYTD CP Plus]),'CP _Plus'[PYTD CP Plus])

measures.name: CP+ 4 Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide('CP _Plus'[YTD CP Plus],4),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Prior 4 Weeks Flag] in {TRUE},DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: CP+ YTD Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide('CP _Plus'[YTD CP Plus],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR])),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[YTD Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: CP+ Curr Wk
measures.expression: CALCULATE('CP _Plus'[YTD CP Plus],'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Prior Week Flag] = 'TRUE')

measures.name: 4wk CP+ Gap
measures.expression: [Weekly Need CP+]-'CP _Plus'[CP+ 4 Wk Average]

source.expression: let    Source = Excel.Workbook(File.Contents('////VSSHR//SHARED//Public//DI and BI//Capacity Dashboard//Capacity Dashboard-CP+.xlsx'), null, true),    Sheet1_Sheet = Source{[Item='Sheet1',Kind='Sheet']}[Data],    #'Promoted Headers' = Table.PromoteHeaders(Sheet1_Sheet, [PromoteAllScalars=true]),    #'Changed Type' = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#'Promoted Headers',{{'RFO_ID', Int64.Type}, {'ZONE_ID', Int64.Type}, {'RFO_Mkt', type text}, {'Type', type text}, {'Year', Int64.Type}, {'Week', Int64.Type}, {'Count', Int64.Type}}),    #'Duplicated Column' = Table.DuplicateColumn(#'Changed Type', 'Year', 'Year - Copy'),    #'Duplicated Column1' = Table.DuplicateColumn(#'Duplicated Column', 'Week', 'Week - Copy'),    #'Merged Columns' = Table.CombineColumns(Table.TransformColumnTypes(#'Duplicated Column1', {{'Year - Copy', type text}, {'Week - Copy', type text}}, 'en-US'),{'Year - Copy', 'Week - Copy'},Combiner.CombineTextByDelimiter('-', QuoteStyle.None),'PerfYear-PerfWeek'),    #'Removed Columns' = Table.RemoveColumns(#'Merged Columns',{'PerfYear-PerfWeek'}),    #'Changed Type1' = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#'Removed Columns',{{'CP+ Scores Above', Int64.Type}, {'Cumulative Counts', Int64.Type}, {'Cumulative CP+ Above', Int64.Type}}),    #'Removed Columns1' = Table.RemoveColumns(#'Changed Type1',{'JOIN VALUE', 'RFO_ID', 'ZONE_ID', 'Type', 'Count', 'Cumulative Counts', 'Cumulative CP+ Above', 'CP+ Above'}),    #'Added Custom' = Table.AddColumn(#'Removed Columns1', 'PerfYrWk_PQ', each Number.ToText([Year])&'-'&Number.ToText([Week])),    #'Removed Columns2' = Table.RemoveColumns(#'Added Custom',{'Year', 'Week'}),    #'Renamed Columns' = Table.RenameColumns(#'Removed Columns2',{{'PerfYrWk_PQ', 'PerfYr_Wk'}})in    #'Renamed Columns'

let    Source = DB2.Database('podwh021:50000', 'podwh021', [HierarchicalNavigation=true, Implementation='Microsoft', Query='SELECT DISTINCT#(lf)DATES_ITRL.DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_NBR,#(lf)DATES_ITRL.DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR,#(lf)max(DATES_ITRL.CAL_DAY_DT) as MAX_Cal_DT#(lf)FROM COMMON.DTRB_PERF_DATES DATES_ITRL#(lf)GROUP BY DATES_ITRL.DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_NBR,#(lf)DATES_ITRL.DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR'])in    Source

columns.name: Product (groups)
columns.expression: SWITCH(  TRUE,  ISBLANK('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[Product]),  '(Blank)',  'ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[Product] IN {'FA',    'FIA',    'SO',    'SPIA',    'VA'},  'Annuity',  'ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[Product] IN {'DI',    'LTC',    'LTC Hybrid',    'LTC Hybrid Single',    'MED_PLANS'},  'Health',  'ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[Product] IN {'PERM_RECURRING',    'SPWL',    'Term',    'UL',    'VUL'},  'Life',  'ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[Product] IN {'ADVANTAGE',    'ADVISOR',    'ADVISOR GUIDED',    'GENESIS',    'IMPACT',    'INCOME FOCUSED',    'SELECT',    'SHEPHERD',    'SHIELD',    'SMA',    'TAN MANAGED ACCOUNTS',    'UMA'},  'Managed Accounts',  'ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[Product] IN {'MF A-SHARE LMBF',    'MF A-SHARES',    'MF S-SHARE LMBF',    'MF S-SHARES',    'NON-PROP MUTUAL FUNDS'},  'Mutual Funds',  'ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[Product] IN {'TRUST'},  'Trust',  'Other')

measures.name: YTD WID
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'WID',     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: CY ANBP
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),        DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE},        ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'ANBP')

measures.name: CY OtherRev
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),    DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE},     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'OtherRev')

measures.name: PY ANBP
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_Flag] in {TRUE},    ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'ANBP')

measures.name: PY WID
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_Flag] in {TRUE},     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'WID')

measures.name: PY2 ANBP
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_2_Flag] in {TRUE},     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'ANBP')

measures.name: PY2 WID
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_2_Flag] in {TRUE},     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'WID')

measures.name: PYTD ANBP
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'ANBP',     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_PYTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: PYTD WID
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP_OtherRev] = 'WID',     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_PYTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: ANBP YOY Change
measures.expression: DIVIDE(([CY ANBP] - ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD ANBP]),ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD ANBP])

measures.name: WID YOY Change
measures.expression: DIVIDE((ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD WID] - ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD WID]),ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD WID])

measures.name: YTD OtherRev running total in CalWk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(\t[YTD WID], \tFILTER(\t\tALLSELECTED('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]),\t\tISONORAFTER('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk], MAX('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]), DESC)\t))

measures.name: PYTD OtherRev running total in CalWk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(\t[PYTD WID],\tFILTER(\t\tALLSELECTED('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]),\t\tISONORAFTER('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk], MAX('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]), DESC)\t))

measures.name: PY2 OtherRev running total in CalWk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(\t[PY2 WID],\tFILTER(\t\tALLSELECTED('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]),\t\tISONORAFTER('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk], MAX('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]), DESC)\t))

measures.name: PY OtherRev running total in CalWk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(\t[PY WID],\tFILTER(\t\tALLSELECTED('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]),\t\tISONORAFTER('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk], MAX('ANBP_OtherRev_DD'[CalWk]), DESC)\t))

measures.name: YTD_OtherRev_Cummulative
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD OtherRev running total in CalWk],    DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: ANBP/Appt
measures.expression: divide([CY ANBP],'Appointments/PC/JFW'[YTD Appointments])

measures.name: WID 4 Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD WID],4),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Prior 4 Weeks Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: WID Curr Wk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD WID],'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_TXT]='PREVIOUS')

measures.name: OtherREV YTD Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD WID],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_NBR])),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: ANBP 4 Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[CY ANBP],4),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Prior 4 Weeks Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: ANBP Curr Wk
measures.expression: CALCULATE(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[CY ANBP],'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_TXT] = 'PREVIOUS')

measures.name: ANBP YTD Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[CY ANBP],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_WK_NBR])),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Cal_YTD_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: 4wk ANBP Gap
measures.expression: YTD_GOALS_DD[Weekly Need ANBP]-ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP 4 Wk Average]

measures.name: 4wk Other Rev Gap
measures.expression: YTD_GOALS_DD[Weekly Need WID]-ANBP_OtherRev_DD[WID 4 Wk Average]

measures.name: 4wk ANBP (LH) Gap
measures.expression: YTD_GOALS_DD[Weekly Need ANBP (LH)]-ANBP_OtherRev_DD[ANBP 4 Wk Average]

measures.name: YTD Total Sales
measures.expression: ANBP_OtherRev_DD[CY ANBP]+ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD WID]

measures.name: Total Sales YOY Change
measures.expression: DIVIDE((ANBP_OtherRev_DD[YTD Total Sales] - ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD Total Sales]),ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD Total Sales])

measures.name: PYTD Total Sales
measures.expression: ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD ANBP]+ANBP_OtherRev_DD[PYTD WID]

measures.name: PY Total Sales
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: PY2 Total Sales
measures.expression: CALCULATE(     sum(ANBP_OtherRev_DD[Value]),     DTRB_PERF_DATES[Cal_Prior_Year_2_Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: Received YTD

measures.name: Prior Year NC
measures.expression: CALCULATE( sum('New Clients'[FIN_CUST_PNT_VLU]), DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Year Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: Prior Year 2 NC
measures.expression: CALCULATE( sum('New Clients'[FIN_CUST_PNT_VLU]), DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Year 2 Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: PYTD NC
measures.expression: var prev2weeknum = LOOKUPVALUE(DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR],DTRB_PERF_DATES[CAL_DAY_DT],max(DTRB_PERF_DATES[Two Sundays Ago]))ReturnCALCULATE(sum('New Clients'[FIN_CUST_PNT_VLU]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[Prior Year Flag] in {TRUE},DTRB_PERF_DATES[DTRB_PERF_RPT_YR_WK_NBR]<=prev2weeknum)

measures.name: YTD_NC
measures.expression: calculate( sum('New Clients'[FIN_CUST_PNT_VLU]),DTRB_PERF_DATES[YTD Flag two Sundays] in {TRUE})

measures.name: YOY Change NC
measures.expression: (([YTD_NC] - [PYTD NC])/([PYTD NC]))

measures.name: New Client 4 Wk Average
measures.expression: CALCULATE(divide('New Clients'[YTD_NC],4),'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[Prior 4 Weeks Flag NC] in {TRUE},DTRB_PERF_DATES[Current Year Flag] in {TRUE})

measures.name: 4 Wk Gap New Clients
measures.expression: [Weekly Need New Clients]-'New Clients'[New Client 4 Wk Average]

columns.name: Connect within Incentive Period
columns.expression: -- ** IMPORTANT ** Update incentive start & end dates at the beginning of each new round--Round 1: 2/12/24-5/5/24--Round 2: 5/6/24-8/4/24--Round 3: 8/5/24-12/29/24var incentive_start_dt = 'Merge Detail'[Incentive Period Start Date]var incentive_end_dt = 'Merge Detail'[Incentive Period End Date]var connect_dt = 'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date]returnif(ISBLANK(connect_dt), '', if('Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] >= incentive_start_dt && 'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] <= incentive_end_dt, 'Y', 'N'))

columns.name: Referrals Led to Connects
columns.expression: var total = if('Merge Detail'[Connect within Incentive Period] = 'Y', 1, 0)return(if(ISBLANK(total),0,total))

columns.name: Prior Sunday or Before - Connects
columns.expression: if('Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] > 'Merge Detail'[Prior Sunday Date], 'N', 'Y')

columns.name: Incentive Period Start Date
columns.expression: -- ** IMPORTANT ** Update incentive start & end dates at the beginning of each new round--Round 1: 2/12/24-5/5/24--Round 2: 5/6/24-8/4/24--Round 3: 8/5/24-12/29/24date(2024,2,12)

columns.name: Incentive Period End Date
columns.expression: -- ** IMPORTANT ** Update incentive start & end dates at the beginning of each new round--Round 1: 2/12/24-5/5/24--Round 2: 5/6/24-8/4/24--Round 3: 8/5/24-12/29/24date(2024,5,5)

columns.name: Text box - Incentive period
columns.expression: 'Incentive period: ' & 'Merge Detail'[Incentive Period Start Date] & ' - ' & 'Merge Detail'[Incentive Period End Date]

columns.name: Min connect date equal to connect date
columns.expression: if(ISBLANK('Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date]), 'Y',if('Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] = [Min connect date], 'Y', 'N'))

columns.name: Prior Sunday or before (connect or referral)
columns.expression: if(or('Merge Detail'[Prior Sunday or Before - Connects] = 'Y', 'Merge Detail'[Prior Sunday or Before - Referrals] = 'Y'), 'Y', 'N')

measures.name: Rank within Tenure Group & TAG
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    RANKX(ALLSELECTED(Producer_Snowflake[EMP_ID]), [YTD Referrals Led to Connects], , DESC),    all(Producer_Snowflake[EMP_NM]),    all(Producer_Snowflake[MVP with Leader]),    all(Producer_Snowflake[MARKET]),    ALL(Producer_Snowflake[Market with Leader]),    all(Producer_Snowflake[Team Purpose Description]),    all(Producer_Snowflake[Team Name]))

measures.name: YTD Referrals
measures.expression: var total=  CALCULATE    (DISTINCTCOUNT('Merge Detail'[CIF_ID]),    'Merge Detail'[Prior Sunday or Before - Referrals] = 'Y')ReturnIF(ISBLANK(total),0,total)

measures.name: Conversion Rate
measures.expression: iferror([YTD Referrals Led to Connects] / [YTD Referrals], 'N/A')

measures.name: YTD Referrals Led to Connects
measures.expression: var __measure =     CALCULATE(        [Number of Min & Max Connect Dates Rows with Connect within Incentive Period NEW]        , Dates[Prior Sunday or Before] = 'Y'    )return__measure + 0

measures.name: Min connect date
measures.expression: var CIF_ID = min('Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.ThriventId])var min_date =MINX(FILTER(all('Merge Detail'), 'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.ThriventId] = CIF_ID), 'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date])returnIF(ISBLANK(CIF_ID),' ',min_date)

measures.name: Min connect date new
measures.expression: IF(ISBLANK([Min connect date]), '', [Min connect date])

measures.name: Top 2 Individuals
measures.expression: var GetIndividuals = VALUES(Producer_Snowflake[EMP_NM])returnCALCULATE([YTD Referrals Led to Connects - INCORRECT],TOPN(2, ALLSELECTED(Producer_Snowflake[EMP_NM]), [YTD Referrals Led to Connects - INCORRECT]), GetIndividuals)--TOPN(2, ALLSELECTED(Producer_Snowflake[EMP_NM]), [YTD Referrals Led to Connects]), GetIndividuals)

measures.name: Rank for Top Individuals
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    RANKX(ALLSELECTED(Producer_Snowflake[EMP_NM]), [YTD Referrals Led to Connects - INCORRECT], , DESC),    --all(Producer_Snowflake[EMP_NM]),    all(Producer_Snowflake[MVP with Leader]),    all(Producer_Snowflake[MARKET]),    ALL(Producer_Snowflake[Market with Leader]),    all(Producer_Snowflake[Team Purpose Description]),    all(Producer_Snowflake[Team Name]))

measures.name: YTD Referrals Led to Connects - INCORRECT
measures.expression: var total =    CALCULATE(        sum('Merge Detail'[Referrals Led to Connects]),        'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] <= 'Merge Detail'[Prior Sunday Date])returnif(ISBLANK(total),0,total)

measures.name: Number of Min & Max Connect Dates Rows with Connect within Incentive Period NEW

columns.name: Connect within Incentive Period (2)
columns.expression: -- ** IMPORTANT ** Update incentive start & end dates at the beginning of each new round--Round 1: 2/12/24-5/5/24--Round 2: 5/6/24-8/4/24--Round 3: 8/5/24-12/29/24var incentive_start_dt = 'Merge Detail (2)'[Incentive Period Start Date (2)]var incentive_end_dt = 'Merge Detail (2)'[Incentive Period End Date (2)]var connect_dt = 'Merge Detail (2)'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date]returnif(ISBLANK(connect_dt), '', if('Merge Detail (2)'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] >= incentive_start_dt && 'Merge Detail (2)'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] <= incentive_end_dt, 'Y', 'N'))

columns.name: Incentive Period End Date (2)
columns.expression: -- ** IMPORTANT ** Update incentive start & end dates at the beginning of each new round--Round 1: 2/12/24-5/5/24--Round 2: 5/6/24-8/4/24--Round 3: 8/5/24-12/29/24date(2024,5,5)

columns.name: Incentive Period Start Date (2)
columns.expression: -- ** IMPORTANT ** Update incentive start & end dates at the beginning of each new round--Round 1: 2/12/24-5/5/24--Round 2: 5/6/24-8/4/24--Round 3: 8/5/24-12/29/24date(2024,2,12)

columns.name: Min connect date equal to connect date (2)
columns.expression: if(ISBLANK('Merge Detail (2)'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date]), 'Y',if('Merge Detail (2)'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] = [Min connect date (2)], 'Y', 'N'))

columns.name: Prior Sunday or Before - Connects (2)
columns.expression: if('Merge Detail (2)'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] > 'Merge Detail (2)'[Prior Sunday Date (2)], 'N', 'Y')

columns.name: Prior Sunday or before (connect or referral) (2)
columns.expression: if(or('Merge Detail (2)'[Prior Sunday or Before - Connects (2)] = 'Y', 'Merge Detail (2)'[Prior Sunday or Before - Referrals (2)] = 'Y'), 'Y', 'N')

measures.name: Min connect date (2)
measures.expression: var CIF_ID = min('Merge Detail (2)'[Prospect Connects.ThriventId])var min_date =MINX(FILTER(all('Merge Detail (2)'), 'Merge Detail (2)'[Prospect Connects.ThriventId] = CIF_ID), 'Merge Detail (2)'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date])returnIF(ISBLANK(CIF_ID),' ',min_date)

columns.name: Date_EarliestConnectOnOrAfterReferral
columns.expression: --Date on our after referralvar __clientID = 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[Person Dimension Surrogate Key] -- The client ID, stored as a whole number.var __year = VALUE( 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[CalYr_Connect] ) -- The year, stored as a whole number.var __date_LatestRefferalInYear = -- Latest referral date (for the person who was referred) in the year __year and the for the person __clientID.    CALCULATE(        MAX( Referrals[REFR_DT] )        , FILTER(            ALL( Referrals )            , VALUE( Referrals[PERS_DIM_SK] ) = __clientID                && YEAR( Referrals[REFR_DT] ) = __year        )    )var __date_EarlestAppointmentAfterReferral = -- Earliest connect appointment date (for the person who was referred) in the year __year, the person __clientID, and on or after __date_LatestReferralInYear.    CALCULATE(        MIN( 'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] )        , FILTER(            ALL( 'Merge Detail' )            , VALUE( 'Merge Detail'[PERS_DIM_SK] ) = __clientID                && YEAR( 'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] ) = __year                && 'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] >= __date_LatestRefferalInYear                && NOT(ISBLANK( __date_LatestRefferalInYear ))                && 'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] >= date(2024,2,12)        )    )return__date_EarlestAppointmentAfterReferral

columns.name: Date_LatestConnectBeforeFirstReferral
columns.expression: --Date of latest connect appointment before referralvar __clientID = 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[Person Dimension Surrogate Key] -- The client ID, stored as a whole number.var __year = VALUE( 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[CalYr_Connect] ) -- The year, stored as a whole number.var __date_LatestRefferalInYear = -- Latest referral date (for the person who was referred) in the year __year and the for the person __clientID.    CALCULATE(        MAX( Referrals[REFR_DT] )        , FILTER(            ALL( Referrals )            , VALUE( Referrals[PERS_DIM_SK] ) = __clientID                && YEAR( Referrals[REFR_DT] ) = __year        )    )var __date_LatestAppointmentBeforeReferral = -- Latest connect appointment date (for the person who was referred) in the year __year, the person __clientID, before __date_LatestReferralInYear.    CALCULATE(        MAX( 'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] )        , FILTER(            ALL( 'Merge Detail' )            , VALUE( 'Merge Detail'[PERS_DIM_SK] ) = __clientID                && YEAR( 'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] ) = __year                && 'Merge Detail'[Prospect Connects.Appointment Date] < __date_LatestRefferalInYear                && NOT(ISBLANK( __date_LatestRefferalInYear ))        )    )return__date_LatestAppointmentBeforeReferral

columns.name: Connect Date to Use
columns.expression: --If there is a connect after the referral, use the earliest connect on or after referral.  If there is no connect after the referral, use the latest connect before referral.var __date_EarliestConnectOnOrAfterReferral = 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[Date_EarliestConnectOnOrAfterReferral]var __date_LatestConnectBeforeFirstReferral = 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[Date_LatestConnectBeforeFirstReferral]var __date_ConnectDateToUse =    CALCULATE(        if(AND(__date_EarliestConnectOnOrAfterReferral = blank(), __date_LatestConnectBeforeFirstReferral = blank())        , blank()        , if(and(__date_EarliestConnectOnOrAfterReferral <> blank(), __date_LatestConnectBeforeFirstReferral = blank()), __date_EarliestConnectOnOrAfterReferral        , if(and(__date_EarliestConnectOnOrAfterReferral <> blank(), __date_LatestConnectBeforeFirstReferral <> blank()), __date_EarliestConnectOnOrAfterReferral        , if(and(__date_EarliestConnectOnOrAfterReferral = blank(), __date_LatestConnectBeforeFirstReferral <> blank()), __date_LatestConnectBeforeFirstReferral        )        )        )        ))RETURN__date_ConnectDateToUse

columns.name: Connect within Incentive Period NEW
columns.expression: -- ** IMPORTANT ** Update incentive start & end dates at the beginning of each new round--Round 1: 2/12/24-5/5/24--Round 2: 5/6/24-8/4/24--Round 3: 8/5/24-12/29/24var __date_incentive_start = date(2024,2,12)var __date_incentive_end = date(2024,5,5)var __date_connect = 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[Connect Date to Use]returnif(ISBLANK(__date_connect), ''    , if(__date_connect >= __date_incentive_start && __date_connect <= __date_incentive_end, 'Y', 'N'))

measures.name: Number of Clients with Connect Date On or AFter Referral Date
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    DISTINCTCOUNT( 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[Person Dimension Surrogate Key] )    , NOT( ISBLANK( 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[Date_EarliestConnectOnOrAfterReferral] ) ))

measures.name: Number of Clients with Connect Date Only Before Referral Date
measures.expression: CALCULATE(    DISTINCTCOUNT( 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[Person Dimension Surrogate Key] )    , NOT( ISBLANK( 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[Date_LatestConnectBeforeFirstReferral] ) )        && ISBLANK( 'Min & Max Connect Dates'[Date_EarliestConnectOnOrAfterReferral] ))

measures.name: Total Grid Per Appt
measures.expression: var total_grid = Calculate(sum('Sales'[Grid Credit Amount]),'Sales'[Distribution Performance Reporting Year Number] = year(today()))  var total_grid_team = Calculate(sum('Sales'[Grid Credit Amount]), 'Sales'[TeamSale_Ind] = 'Y', 'Sales'[Distribution Performance Reporting Year Number] = year(today()))  var ytd_appts = calculate(DISTINCTCOUNT('Vital Stats DB Appointment Detail'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key]), YEAR('Vital Stats DB Appointment Detail'[Appointment Date]) = YEAR(TODAY()), 'Vital Stats DB Appointment Detail'[Appointment Date] < today())  --var _total = total_grid/ytd_appts  var _indvtotal = total_grid/ytd_appts  var _teamtotal = total_grid_team/ytd_apptsReturn--Divide(total_grid,ytd_appts,0)+0IF([TeamNmFiltered] = 1, IF(ISBLANK(_teamtotal),0,_teamtotal), IF(ISBLANK(_indvtotal),0,_indvtotal))

measures.name: Avg Appt Total
measures.expression: var _avgtotal = AVERAGE([Appointment Count]) +0Return_avgtotal--IF(ISBLANK(_avgtotal),0,_avgtotal)

measures.name: Clients Per Appt
measures.expression: var _pastyr =LOOKUPVALUE('DTRB_PERF_DATES'[CAL_DAY_DT], 'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[CAL_DAY_DT], today()-366)RETURNCALCULATE(sum('DM_01 Vital Stats Summary Fact'[Person Appointment Count]) / sum('DM_01 Vital Stats Summary Fact'[Appointment Count]), 'DTRB_PERF_DATES'[CAL_DAY_DT] > _pastyr)

measures.name: TGR Case Size
measures.expression: var _TGRamt =SUM('DM_01 Vital Stats Summary Fact'[GRID Credit Amount])  var _TGRCtrcCount =SUM('DM_01 Vital Stats Summary Fact'[GRID Credit Contract Count])  var _total = DIVIDE(_TGRamt,_TGRCtrcCount,0)RETURNIF(ISBLANK(_total),0,_total)

measures.name: TGR Contract Efficiency
measures.expression: var _TGRContractCount =SUM('DM_01 Vital Stats Summary Fact'[GRID Credit Contract Count])  var _PersonContractCount = SUM('DM_01 Vital Stats Summary Fact'[Person Contract Grid Credit Count])RETURNDIVIDE(_TGRContractCount,_PersonContractCount,0)

measures.name: TGR Total Close Rate
measures.expression: var _TGR_Person_Count = SUM('DM_01 Vital Stats Summary Fact'[Person Contract Grid Credit Count])  var _PersonCount = SUM('DM_01 Vital Stats Summary Fact'[Person Count])  var _total = Divide(_TGR_Person_Count,_PersonCount,0)ReturnIF(ISBLANK(_total),0,_total)

measures.name: Total Future Prospect Connect
measures.expression: CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('Future Prospect Connects'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key]))

measures.name: Future PC Wk1
measures.expression: CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('Future Prospect Connects'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key])+0,  'Future Prospect Connects'[Future Prospect Connect Week] = 'Next 7 days')

measures.name: Future PC Wk2
measures.expression: CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('Future Prospect Connects'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key])+0,  'Future Prospect Connects'[Future Prospect Connect Week] = 'Next 8-14 days')

measures.name: Future PC Wk3
measures.expression: CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('Future Prospect Connects'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key])+0,  'Future Prospect Connects'[Future Prospect Connect Week] = 'Next 15-21 days')

measures.name: Future PC Wk4
measures.expression: CALCULATE(DISTINCTCOUNT('Future Prospect Connects'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key])+0,  'Future Prospect Connects'[Future Prospect Connect Week] = 'Next 22-28 days')

measures.name: Message_txtPCAppts
measures.expression: if(ISBLANK(DISTINCTCOUNT('Future Prospect Connects'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key])), 'There are no future prospect connect appointments scheduled','')

measures.name: ShowHideFuturePCAppts
measures.expression: IF(DISTINCTCOUNT('Future Prospect Connects'[Appointment Dimension Surrogate Key]) > 0,'#1C00ff00','White')

measures.name: Alert Msg
measures.expression: var _alertmsg = LOOKUPVALUE('Whats New_ Alert Msg'[Message],'Whats New_ Alert Msg'[Message Description],'ALERT!')RETURNif(_alertmsg <> BLANK(), _alertmsg,'')

measures.name: Show Alert Msg Box
measures.expression: var _alertmsg = LOOKUPVALUE('Whats New_ Alert Msg'[Message],'Whats New_ Alert Msg'[Message Description],'ALERT!')RETURNif(_alertmsg<>BLANK(),1,0)

measures.name: Show What's New Msg Box
measures.expression: var _enddate = LOOKUPVALUE('Whats New_ Alert Msg'[End Date],'Whats New_ Alert Msg'[Message Description],'What's New')RETURNif(today() <= _enddate,1,0)

measures.name: What's New Msg

columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Year]='CY',if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks',    'Green',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks',    if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total]+'Pending RR48'[Pending Amount Total]>=4000, 'Green',if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total]+'Pending RR48'[Pending Amount Total]>=1000,'Yellow','Red')),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks',    if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total]>=8000, 'Green',if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total]+'Pending RR48'[Pending Amount Total]>=2000,'Yellow','Red')),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks',    if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total]>=12000, 'Green',if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total]>=1000,'Yellow','Red')),    'NA')))),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks',    'Green',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks',    if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total-PY]+'Pending RR48'[Pending Amount-PY]>=4000, 'Green',if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total-PY]+'Pending RR48'[Pending Amount-PY]>=1000,'Yellow','Red')),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks',    if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total-PY]>=8000, 'Green',if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total-PY]+'Pending RR48'[Pending Amount-PY]>=2000,'Yellow','Red')),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks',    if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total-PY]>=12000, 'Green',if('GridRevenue - Snowflake_RR48'[New Grid Revenue Total-PY]>=1000,'Yellow','Red')),    'NA')))))

columns.name: New Client Status
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Year]='CY',if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks',    'Green',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks',    if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients]>=5, 'Green',if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients]>=1,'Yellow','Red')),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks',    if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients]>=7.5, 'Green',if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients]>=2,'Yellow','Red')),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks',    if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients]>=10, 'Green',if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients]>=4,'Yellow','Red')),    'NA')))),if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks',    'Green',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks',    if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients-PY]>=5,'Green',if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients-PY]>=1,'Yellow','Red')),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks',    if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients-PY]>=7.5, 'Green',if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients-PY]>=2,'Yellow','Red')),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks',    if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients-PY]>=10, 'Green',if('NFC RR48'[Total New Clients-PY]>=4,'Yellow','Red')),    'NA')))))

columns.name: Advice Status
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks',    if('CLIENT_HHLD'[Households with Goals - CIF]>1, 'Green',if('CLIENT_HHLD'[Households with Goals - CIF]=1,'Yellow','Red')),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks',    if('CLIENT_HHLD'[Households with Goals - CIF]>4, 'Green',if('CLIENT_HHLD'[Households with Goals - CIF]=4,'Yellow','Red')),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks',    if('CLIENT_HHLD'[Households with Goals - CIF]>6, 'Green',if('CLIENT_HHLD'[Households with Goals - CIF]=6,'Yellow','Red')),    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks',    if('CLIENT_HHLD'[Households with Goals - CIF]>10, 'Green',if('CLIENT_HHLD'[Households with Goals - CIF]=10,'Yellow','Red'))    ,'NA'))))

columns.name: Weeks Until Minimum
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks',    5-'RR_In_and_Out'[Tenure Week]+1,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks',    9-'RR_In_and_Out'[Tenure Week]+1,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks',    13-'RR_In_and_Out'[Tenure Week]+1,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks',    17-'RR_In_and_Out'[Tenure Week]+1,    9999))))

columns.name: Time Until Minimum
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Weeks Until Minimum]=1,'<1 Week',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Weeks Until Minimum]=2,'1-2 Weeks',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Weeks Until Minimum]=3,'2-3 Weeks',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Weeks Until Minimum]=4,'3-4 Weeks',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Weeks Until Minimum]=5,'4-5 Weeks',    'NA')))))

columns.name: Appointment Min
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks', 16,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks', 32,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks', 48,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks', 64,64))))

columns.name: New Client Min
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks',    0,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks',1,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks',2,     if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks',4,     4))))

columns.name: Prod Min
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks','None',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks', '750 (pend/iss)',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks', '2,000 (pend/iss)',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks', '1,500 (issued)','1,500 (issued)'))))

columns.name: Advice Min
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks',1,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks', 4,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks', 6,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks',10,10))))

columns.name: JFW Status
columns.expression: var _JFW=if(RR_In_and_Out[Year]='CY',if(('Vitals RR48'[Total JFW]/'Vitals RR48'[Total Appointments])>0.95, 'Green',if(('Vitals RR48'[Total JFW]/'Vitals RR48'[Total Appointments])>0.8,'Yellow','Red')),if(('Vitals RR48'[PY Total JFW]/'Vitals RR48'[Total Appointments - PY])>0.95, 'Green',if(('Vitals RR48'[PY Total JFW]/'Vitals RR48'[Total Appointments - PY])>0.8,'Yellow','Red')))returnif(if(RR_In_and_Out[Year]='CY','Vitals RR48'[Total Appointments],'Vitals RR48'[Total Appointments - PY])=0,'Red',if(isblank(_JFW),'Red',_JFW))

columns.name: JFW Percent
columns.expression: var _JFW=if(RR_In_and_Out[Year]='CY','Vitals RR48'[Total JFW],'Vitals RR48'[PY Total JFW])/if(RR_In_and_Out[Year]='CY','Vitals RR48'[Total Appointments],'Vitals RR48'[Total Appointments - PY])returnif(if(RR_In_and_Out[Year]='CY','Vitals RR48'[Total Appointments],'Vitals RR48'[Total Appointments - PY])=0,0,if(isblank(_JFW),0,_JFW))

columns.name: Tenure Week Sort
columns.expression: if(RR_In_and_Out[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks',1,if(RR_In_and_Out[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks', 2,if(RR_In_and_Out[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks',3,if(RR_In_and_Out[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks',4,5))))

columns.name: Applications Status
columns.expression: if(RR_In_and_Out[Year]='CY',if([New Pending Applications]>=10,'10+ apps',if([New Pending Applications]>=5,'5-10 apps',if([New Pending Applications]>=0,'0-5 apps','NA'))),if([PY Pending Applications]>=10,'10+ apps',if([PY Pending Applications]>=5,'5-10 apps',if([PY Pending Applications]>=0,'0-5 apps','NA'))))

columns.name: Appointment Target
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks', 32,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks', 64,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks', 96,    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks', 128,128))))

columns.name: New Client Target
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks',    '0',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks','5',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks','7.5',     if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks','10',     '10'))))

columns.name: Prod Target
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks','None',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks', '4,000 (pend/iss)',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks', '6,000 (issued)',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks', '9,000 (issued)','9,000 (issued)'))))

columns.name: Applications Status (written)
columns.expression: if(RR_In_and_Out[Year]='CY',if([Written Applications]>=10,'10+ apps',if([Written Applications]>=5,'5-10 apps',if([Written Applications]>=0,'0-5 apps','NA'))),if([Written Applications]>=10,'10+ apps',if([Written Applications]>=5,'5-10 apps',if([Written Applications]>=0,'0-5 apps','NA'))))

columns.name: Applications Target
columns.expression: if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='0-5 weeks','None',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='5-9 weeks', '8 (pend/iss)',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='9-13 weeks', '12 (issued)',    if('RR_In_and_Out'[Red Role Tenure]='13-17 weeks', '16 (issued)','16 (issued)'))))
